Dialogue: 0.0:00:02.00.0:00:07.00.Default..0.0.0..Downloaded from\NYTS.MX
Dialogue: 0.0:00:08.00.0:00:13.00.Default..0.0.0..Official YIFY movies site:\NYTS.MX
Dialogue: 0.0:00:18.23.0:00:19.94.Default..0.0.0..[Ed. on tape recorder]\N{\i1}My name is Ed Warren.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:00:20.02.0:00:23.61.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}here with my wife. Lorraine.{\i0}\N{\i1}and Victoria Grainger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:00:24.48.0:00:26.78.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}It's April 20th. 1964.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:00:28.11.0:00:33.33.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Victoria… when did you first notice{\i0}\N{\i1}these supernatural occurrences?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:00:36.12.0:00:37.66.Default..0.0.0..[Victoria] {\i1}I'm sorry.{\i0}\N{\i1}I don't know how to do this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:00:38.54.0:00:40.67.Default..0.0.0..[Ed] {\i1}Why don't you just{\i0}\N{\i1}take us back to the beginning?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:00:40.75.0:00:42.75.Default..0.0.0..[rain pattering]
Dialogue: 0.0:00:44.04.0:00:46.42.Default..0.0.0..[Victoria] {\i1}My father thought{\i0}\N{\i1}something was following him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:00:48.26.0:00:49.88.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Something he couldn't see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:00:51.80.0:00:54.10.Default..0.0.0..He'd lock the doors at night.\Nand the next morning. they…
Dialogue: 0.0:00:54.18.0:00:55.31.Default..0.0.0..[pattering fades]
Dialogue: 0.0:00:55.39.0:00:56.68.Default..0.0.0..…they'd be open.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:01.02.0:01:02.40.Default..0.0.0..[shuddering breath]
Dialogue: 0.0:01:02.77.0:01:05.27.Default..0.0.0..Then he started hearing… [inhales]
Dialogue: 0.0:01:06.32.0:01:07.32.Default..0.0.0..…voices.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:08.40.0:01:09.70.Default..0.0.0..I didn't believe him.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:11.53.0:01:13.20.Default..0.0.0..I thought he was getting old. you know?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:17.33.0:01:18.87.Default..0.0.0..But then I came in one day. and…
Dialogue: 0.0:01:20.25.0:01:22.75.Default..0.0.0..[shuddering breaths]
Dialogue: 0.0:01:23.08.0:01:24.21.Default..0.0.0..I found him.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:25.17.0:01:26.67.Default..0.0.0..[rope creaking]
Dialogue: 0.0:01:27.76.0:01:29.67.Default..0.0.0..[shrieks] Dad!
Dialogue: 0.0:01:29.76.0:01:32.13.Default..0.0.0..[Victoria sobbing]
Dialogue: 0.0:01:32.22.0:01:34.26.Default..0.0.0..It was so quiet here after he was gone.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:37.56.0:01:40.06.Default..0.0.0..But then something changed.\N[deep breath]
Dialogue: 0.0:01:41.81.0:01:43.10.Default..0.0.0..I could feel it.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:44.98.0:01:46.94.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}This really strong feeling. like…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:01:47.02.0:01:48.90.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.0:01:48.98.0:01:50.57.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}…like I'm being watched.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:01:51.90.0:01:53.91.Default..0.0.0..[faint growl]
Dialogue: 0.0:02:03.33.0:02:04.79.Default..0.0.0..There's something in there.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:06.88.0:02:08.25.Default..0.0.0..And when I'm here alone…
Dialogue: 0.0:02:09.88.0:02:11.38.Default..0.0.0..and it's very quiet…
Dialogue: 0.0:02:13.47.0:02:15.01.Default..0.0.0..…it calls to me.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:28.11.0:02:29.15.Default..0.0.0..[tape recorder clicks]
Dialogue: 0.0:02:35.28.0:02:36.74.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine grunts]
Dialogue: 0.0:02:40.37.0:02:42.37.Default..0.0.0..[clock ticking]
Dialogue: 0.0:02:44.16.0:02:46.25.Default..0.0.0..[door creaks]
Dialogue: 0.0:02:46.33.0:02:48.34.Default..0.0.0..[rain pattering]
Dialogue: 0.0:02:50.00.0:02:51.01.Default..0.0.0..Hon…
Dialogue: 0.0:02:52.55.0:02:55.18.Default..0.0.0..I don't know.\NI don't have a good feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:55.26.0:02:58.18.Default..0.0.0..Ed. I can do this.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:10.02.0:03:12.03.Default..0.0.0..[rain pattering]
Dialogue: 0.0:03:15.74.0:03:17.74.Default..0.0.0..[clock ticking]
Dialogue: 0.0:03:19.91.0:03:21.91.Default..0.0.0..[syncopated ticking]
Dialogue: 0.0:03:28.88.0:03:30.75.Default..0.0.0..[clock chimes]
Dialogue: 0.0:03:39.72.0:03:41.14.Default..0.0.0..[ticking and chiming halts]
Dialogue: 0.0:03:45.52.0:03:47.98.Default..0.0.0..[eerie voice whispers] {\i1}Lorraine…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:04:03.62.0:04:06.58.Default..0.0.0..[rumbling]
Dialogue: 0.0:04:11.88.0:04:13.88.Default..0.0.0..[nervous breathing]
Dialogue: 0.0:04:17.55.0:04:19.55.Default..0.0.0..My name is Lorraine Warren.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:20.59.0:04:22.85.Default..0.0.0..- [low rumbling]\N- [foundations creaking]
Dialogue: 0.0:04:22.93.0:04:24.18.Default..0.0.0..I'm here to help.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:29.10.0:04:32.86.Default..0.0.0..I can… [exhaling] feel your spirit.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:36.74.0:04:37.95.Default..0.0.0..Your fear.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:42.37.0:04:44.37.Default..0.0.0..There's something else.\N[breath shuddering]
Dialogue: 0.0:04:45.08.0:04:47.08.Default..0.0.0..[creaking]
Dialogue: 0.0:04:52.50.0:04:53.92.Default..0.0.0..[shuddering exhale]
Dialogue: 0.0:04:57.42.0:04:59.05.Default..0.0.0..[whispering] What are you?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:14.44.0:05:16.32.Default..0.0.0..[gasping]
Dialogue: 0.0:05:16.94.0:05:18.36.Default..0.0.0..[low snarl]
Dialogue: 0.0:05:18.94.0:05:20.20.Default..0.0.0..[screaming]
Dialogue: 0.0:05:20.28.0:05:21.28.Default..0.0.0..[gasps]
Dialogue: 0.0:05:21.70.0:05:22.74.Default..0.0.0..[cries out]
Dialogue: 0.0:05:24.16.0:05:25.74.Default..0.0.0..- [Lorraine] Ed!\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 0.0:05:26.41.0:05:28.04.Default..0.0.0..- Lorraine! Lorraine?\N- [Lorraine] Ed!
Dialogue: 0.0:05:28.12.0:05:30.37.Default..0.0.0..- [Lorraine panting]\N- Lorraine. what happened?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:33.46.0:05:34.59.Default..0.0.0..The baby!
Dialogue: 0.0:05:40.30.0:05:42.63.Default..0.0.0..- [pained groan]\N- The hospital's ten minutes away!
Dialogue: 0.0:05:42.72.0:05:43.93.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine moaning]
Dialogue: 0.0:05:44.01.0:05:45.35.Default..0.0.0..What was that back there?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:45.43.0:05:46.31.Default..0.0.0..I don't know!
Dialogue: 0.0:05:47.60.0:05:49.18.Default..0.0.0..[engine roars]
Dialogue: 0.0:05:52.52.0:05:54.23.Default..0.0.0..[wheezing]
Dialogue: 0.0:05:54.31.0:05:57.86.Default..0.0.0..There was something… [wheezes]\Nin the room. [wheezes]
Dialogue: 0.0:05:57.94.0:05:59.23.Default..0.0.0..In the mirror.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:59.32.0:06:00.65.Default..0.0.0..I don't know.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:01.86.0:06:03.86.Default..0.0.0..[wails]
Dialogue: 0.0:06:07.24.0:06:08.91.Default..0.0.0..[frantic gasping]
Dialogue: 0.0:06:08.99.0:06:10.70.Default..0.0.0..- [nurse] When's the baby due?\N- May. She's early!
Dialogue: 0.0:06:10.79.0:06:11.96.Default..0.0.0..Okay. notify Labor and Delivery.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:12.04.0:06:13.46.Default..0.0.0..We're coming in\Nwith a possible abruption!
Dialogue: 0.0:06:13.54.0:06:14.75.Default..0.0.0..- She's abrupting.\N- [Ed] It's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:14.83.0:06:17.04.Default..0.0.0..Ed! Something's wrong. I can feel it!
Dialogue: 0.0:06:17.13.0:06:19.42.Default..0.0.0..- It's okay. It's gonna be all right.\N- Sir? Sir. you have to stay out here.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:19.51.0:06:21.30.Default..0.0.0..- No. Lorraine! Lorraine!\N- Sir! Sir!
Dialogue: 0.0:06:21.38.0:06:23.18.Default..0.0.0..Lorraine! Lorraine!
Dialogue: 0.0:06:23.51.0:06:24.72.Default..0.0.0..We need to get the baby out.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:24.80.0:06:26.47.Default..0.0.0..- You've gotta push.\N- [moans]
Dialogue: 0.0:06:26.55.0:06:28.64.Default..0.0.0..[strains]
Dialogue: 0.0:06:30.02.0:06:31.56.Default..0.0.0..[monitor beeping]
Dialogue: 0.0:06:32.14.0:06:33.60.Default..0.0.0..She's losing blood.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:33.69.0:06:35.56.Default..0.0.0..- We got blood on the way?\N- [nurse] Yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:35.65.0:06:36.61.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.0:06:36.69.0:06:37.52.Default..0.0.0..Where's Ed?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:37.61.0:06:38.94.Default..0.0.0..- How's the baby?\N- [Lorraine groans]
Dialogue: 0.0:06:40.03.0:06:41.19.Default..0.0.0..- [doctor] What's her vitals?\N- Where's Ed?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:41.28.0:06:43.70.Default..0.0.0..[nurse] Pulse. 130.\NPressure. 80 over 40.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:43.78.0:06:45.20.Default..0.0.0..- [boom]\N- Damn it!
Dialogue: 0.0:06:45.28.0:06:46.70.Default..0.0.0..[pants]
Dialogue: 0.0:06:47.28.0:06:48.53.Default..0.0.0..[doctor] Get me a flashlight.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:49.41.0:06:50.99.Default..0.0.0..[equipment rattling]
Dialogue: 0.0:06:51.08.0:06:52.66.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.0:06:53.12.0:06:55.12.Default..0.0.0..[rumbling]
Dialogue: 0.0:06:55.50.0:06:59.59.Default..0.0.0..- [panting]\N- [guttural growl]
Dialogue: 0.0:07:03.34.0:07:05.93.Default..0.0.0..[inhales] Something's here!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:06.22.0:07:08.39.Default..0.0.0..[low snarl]
Dialogue: 0.0:07:08.47.0:07:10.47.Default..0.0.0..[deep growling]
Dialogue: 0.0:07:11.64.0:07:12.60.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.0:07:13.98.0:07:15.98.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.0:07:18.69.0:07:22.15.Default..0.0.0..[rapid panting]
Dialogue: 0.0:07:23.57.0:07:25.57.Default..0.0.0..[frantic breathing]
Dialogue: 0.0:07:25.65.0:07:29.16.Default..0.0.0..[growling]
Dialogue: 0.0:07:32.41.0:07:33.91.Default..0.0.0..- Power's out! Lorraine!\N- [nurse shouting]
Dialogue: 0.0:07:34.00.0:07:35.33.Default..0.0.0..- No. no! Lorraine?\N- Ed!
Dialogue: 0.0:07:35.41.0:07:37.37.Default..0.0.0..Please-- No. please.\NI need to talk to my wife.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:37.46.0:07:39.25.Default..0.0.0..[thunder rumbling]
Dialogue: 0.0:07:39.33.0:07:40.34.Default..0.0.0..Don't get in the way.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:41.75.0:07:44.92.Default..0.0.0..Ed… [panting]\NDon't let it hurt the baby.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:46.22.0:07:47.59.Default..0.0.0..Don't let what hurt the baby?
Dialogue: 0.0:07:48.64.0:07:49.47.Default..0.0.0..Please.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:49.55.0:07:50.85.Default..0.0.0..All right. the head's right here.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:50.93.0:07:52.93.Default..0.0.0..- [Lorraine pants]\N- You need to push. Mrs. Warren.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:53.02.0:07:54.52.Default..0.0.0..[strains]
Dialogue: 0.0:07:54.60.0:07:56.19.Default..0.0.0..[wails]
Dialogue: 0.0:07:56.27.0:07:58.31.Default..0.0.0..Stop pushing! The head's out.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:58.40.0:08:00.48.Default..0.0.0..- [wails]\N- The cord's around the neck.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:01.15.0:08:02.61.Default..0.0.0..I need two clamps and scissors.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:03.23.0:08:04.61.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine gasps raggedly]
Dialogue: 0.0:08:04.69.0:08:06.99.Default..0.0.0..What? [pants] What'd he say?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:07.07.0:08:07.95.Default..0.0.0..[gasps]
Dialogue: 0.0:08:08.78.0:08:09.99.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine] What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:10.07.0:08:10.91.Default..0.0.0..One more push.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:10.99.0:08:12.66.Default..0.0.0..- We gotta get this baby out.\N- [pained gasps]
Dialogue: 0.0:08:12.74.0:08:13.99.Default..0.0.0..[whispering] Okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:14.08.0:08:16.04.Default..0.0.0..- It's coming. It's coming.\N- [wails]
Dialogue: 0.0:08:18.58.0:08:20.50.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine groans]
Dialogue: 0.0:08:20.58.0:08:22.59.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.0:08:25.88.0:08:26.88.Default..0.0.0..[thunder rumbling]
Dialogue: 0.0:08:26.97.0:08:28.88.Default..0.0.0..[doctor] I need that light.\NShe's still bleeding.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:28.97.0:08:30.34.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine] Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:30.43.0:08:31.89.Default..0.0.0..[breathless] What's wrong with her?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:32.64.0:08:34.10.Default..0.0.0..- [Lorraine] Something's wrong!\N- Do you need help?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:34.18.0:08:35.22.Default..0.0.0..Please.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:36.98.0:08:38.39.Default..0.0.0..Doctor. what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:39.06.0:08:40.90.Default..0.0.0..Doctor. what's happening? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:42.15.0:08:42.90.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine whimpers]
Dialogue: 0.0:08:48.11.0:08:49.45.Default..0.0.0..[panicked breaths]
Dialogue: 0.0:08:51.78.0:08:54.79.Default..0.0.0..[thunder rumbling]
Dialogue: 0.0:08:55.87.0:08:57.33.Default..0.0.0..[metal clatters]
Dialogue: 0.0:09:02.54.0:09:04.17.Default..0.0.0..[voice breaking] Give me my baby.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:06.88.0:09:09.01.Default..0.0.0..Give me my baby!
Dialogue: 0.0:09:10.59.0:09:11.93.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine whimpers]
Dialogue: 0.0:09:22.23.0:09:23.19.Default..0.0.0..I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:23.27.0:09:25.57.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine sighs]
Dialogue: 0.0:09:29.70.0:09:31.61.Default..0.0.0..Oh. [cries]
Dialogue: 0.0:09:31.70.0:09:33.82.Default..0.0.0..[whispers] Oh.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:37.29.0:09:38.58.Default..0.0.0..God.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:38.66.0:09:40.75.Default..0.0.0..Oh. please. Heavenly Father.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:40.83.0:09:42.75.Default..0.0.0..Please. bring her back. [sniffles]
Dialogue: 0.0:09:42.83.0:09:43.83.Default..0.0.0..[Ed. whispers] Oh. God.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:45.29.0:09:46.96.Default..0.0.0..Please. bring her back.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:47.05.0:09:48.30.Default..0.0.0..[Ed] Oh. God.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:49.97.0:09:52.59.Default..0.0.0..[sobbing] Heavenly father. please…
Dialogue: 0.0:09:54.34.0:09:56.60.Default..0.0.0..Please. bring her back.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:58.06.0:10:00.23.Default..0.0.0..Please. bring her back.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:01.02.0:10:02.89.Default..0.0.0..Please. bring her back.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:03.85.0:10:06.06.Default..0.0.0..Oh. God. please.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:07.27.0:10:10.86.Default..0.0.0..Please. Please…
Dialogue: 0.0:10:11.95.0:10:14.45.Default..0.0.0..[baby grunts. cries]
Dialogue: 0.0:10:14.53.0:10:16.53.Default..0.0.0..- [gasping]\N- [baby crying]
Dialogue: 0.0:10:17.33.0:10:19.29.Default..0.0.0..Oh. my God! Oh!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:19.37.0:10:21.12.Default..0.0.0..[baby crying]
Dialogue: 0.0:10:21.79.0:10:23.79.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine shuddering. laughing]
Dialogue: 0.0:10:25.13.0:10:27.13.Default..0.0.0..[gasping]
Dialogue: 0.0:10:27.63.0:10:29.63.Default..0.0.0..[laughter]
Dialogue: 0.0:10:30.38.0:10:31.55.Default..0.0.0..Oh… oh!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:31.63.0:10:33.63.Default..0.0.0..[crying]
Dialogue: 0.0:10:33.72.0:10:35.39.Default..0.0.0..[exhales]
Dialogue: 0.0:10:40.60.0:10:44.77.Default..0.0.0..- [kisses] Oh.\N- [cries]
Dialogue: 0.0:10:45.73.0:10:46.56.Default..0.0.0..What's her name?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:49.69.0:10:51.40.Default..0.0.0..[laughs] Her name is Judy.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:53.32.0:10:54.45.Default..0.0.0..Judy Warren.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:56.24.0:10:58.41.Default..0.0.0..[laughs. sniffles]
Dialogue: 0.0:10:59.20.0:11:01.20.Default..0.0.0..[baby crying]
Dialogue: 0.0:11:06.71.0:11:08.34.Default..0.0.0..[baby grunting]
Dialogue: 0.0:11:10.71.0:11:12.09.Default..0.0.0..[cooing]
Dialogue: 0.0:11:14.13.0:11:15.59.Default..0.0.0..- [gurgles]\N- [Lorraine giggles]
Dialogue: 0.0:11:18.55.0:11:20.10.Default..0.0.0..- [Lorraine chuckling]\N- Come on. Come here.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:20.18.0:11:21.10.Default..0.0.0..Come on. baby.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:21.81.0:11:22.97.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine] So good.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:23.43.0:11:25.10.Default..0.0.0..- [Judy squeals]\N- [both laugh]
Dialogue: 0.0:11:25.19.0:11:26.52.Default..0.0.0..- [Judy laughs]\N- [Lorraine] So good!
Dialogue: 0.0:11:27.06.0:11:29.06.Default..0.0.0..- [Judy screaming]\N- [Ed grunting playfully]
Dialogue: 0.0:11:30.27.0:11:32.28.Default..0.0.0..[all laughing]
Dialogue: 0.0:11:36.78.0:11:38.28.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine chuckles]
Dialogue: 0.0:11:42.20.0:11:43.29.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine chuckles]
Dialogue: 0.0:11:43.37.0:11:45.37.Default..0.0.0..[Judy cries out. giggles]
Dialogue: 0.0:11:46.00.0:11:48.00.Default..0.0.0..[Ed and Judy laugh]
Dialogue: 0.0:11:51.63.0:11:53.42.Default..0.0.0..- [sobbing]\N- [Lorraine] Judy!
Dialogue: 0.0:11:53.51.0:11:55.09.Default..0.0.0..What? Honey.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:55.63.0:11:57.09.Default..0.0.0..[Judy sobs]
Dialogue: 0.0:11:57.18.0:11:58.18.Default..0.0.0..Honey.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:59.51.0:12:03.39.Default..0.0.0..I keep seeing horrible things!\NAnd they won't go away!
Dialogue: 0.0:12:03.47.0:12:05.43.Default..0.0.0..- Oh. hon!\N- [crying]
Dialogue: 0.0:12:05.52.0:12:06.69.Default..0.0.0..All right. all right.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:06.77.0:12:10.73.Default..0.0.0..Just shut it out.\Njust like I taught you. okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:10.81.0:12:12.52.Default..0.0.0..- Just like I taught you.\N- [Judy sniffles]
Dialogue: 0.0:12:12.61.0:12:15.65.Default..0.0.0..[singing]\N{\i1}♪ Lucy Locket lost her pocket ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:12:15.74.0:12:19.07.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- ♪ Kitty Fisher found it ♪{\i0}\N{\i1}- ♪ Kitty Fisher found it ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:12:19.16.0:12:22.20.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- ♪ Not a penny was there in it ♪{\i0}\N{\i1}- ♪ Not a penny was there in it ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:12:22.28.0:12:25.33.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- ♪ Only ribbon 'round it ♪{\i0}\N{\i1}- ♪ Only ribbon 'round it ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:12:25.41.0:12:29.21.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- ♪ You're not there ♪{\i0}\N{\i1}- ♪ You're not there ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:12:35.51.0:12:38.76.Default..0.0.0..Those things. what if I can't\Nmake them go away?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:43.18.0:12:44.26.Default..0.0.0..You can.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:45.39.0:12:46.27.Default..0.0.0..Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:46.52.0:12:48.89.Default..0.0.0..You can. It's your choice.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:50.90.0:12:52.31.Default..0.0.0..It's your choice. hon.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:53.73.0:12:54.65.Default..0.0.0..Come here.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:56.40.0:12:57.74.Default..0.0.0..I love you.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:58.65.0:12:59.78.Default..0.0.0..I love you. too.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:06.20.0:13:07.75.Default..0.0.0..My baby…
Dialogue: 0.0:13:16.63.0:13:18.05.Default..0.0.0..[inhales deeply]
Dialogue: 0.0:13:18.63.0:13:19.63.Default..0.0.0..[sighs]
Dialogue: 0.0:13:27.56.0:13:29.56.Default..0.0.0..["She Sells Sanctuary"\Nby The Cult playing]
Dialogue: 0.0:13:39.57.0:13:40.40.Default..0.0.0..[man] Come on. boy.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:45.20.0:13:46.37.Default..0.0.0..Good boy.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:46.45.0:13:48.25.Default..0.0.0..Mom told me to get some decorations\Nfrom the attic.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:48.33.0:13:50.08.Default..0.0.0..Well. quickly. Come on. everybody!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:50.16.0:13:52.12.Default..0.0.0..They're not holding Mass just for us!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:52.21.0:13:53.96.Default..0.0.0..Come on. Dad. Turn the TV off.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:54.04.0:13:55.21.Default..0.0.0..[mom] Thank you. honey.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:55.29.0:13:57.50.Default..0.0.0..- Damn it!\N- [dad] Language. Heather!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:58.59.0:13:59.88.Default..0.0.0..Carin. get down from there.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:59.97.0:14:02.09.Default..0.0.0..- Don't forget the camera.\N- It's charged?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:02.18.0:14:03.30.Default..0.0.0..Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:03.39.0:14:04.68.Default..0.0.0..[humming]
Dialogue: 0.0:14:04.76.0:14:05.60.Default..0.0.0..Mom!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:05.68.0:14:07.14.Default..0.0.0..- [mom] Heather. what?\N- It's a disaster!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:07.22.0:14:08.27.Default..0.0.0..Dawn was hogging the bathroom all morning.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:08.35.0:14:09.81.Default..0.0.0..- I was not!\N- Oh. she was!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:09.89.0:14:10.85.Default..0.0.0..There was no hot water left.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:10.93.0:14:12.39.Default..0.0.0..And when I tried to dry my hair.\Nthe outlet blew out!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:12.48.0:14:13.81.Default..0.0.0..Mom. just give me a minute.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:13.90.0:14:16.90.Default..0.0.0..Honey. there's still time\Nto fix your hair. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:16.98.0:14:18.73.Default..0.0.0..And you look so beautiful in this dress!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:18.82.0:14:20.28.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. let's not lie to her. Grandma.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:20.36.0:14:21.74.Default..0.0.0..[shrieks] I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0.0:14:21.82.0:14:23.74.Default..0.0.0..You can't kill her on your confirmation.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:26.16.0:14:28.16.Default..0.0.0..[organ playing gently]
Dialogue: 0.0:14:28.49.0:14:30.04.Default..0.0.0..Milo Evans Roberts.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:30.91.0:14:32.79.Default..0.0.0..Milo Evans Roberts.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:32.87.0:14:35.29.Default..0.0.0..be sealed with the gift\Nof the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:35.38.0:14:36.71.Default..0.0.0..- [Milo] Amen.\N- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:37.50.0:14:39.30.Default..0.0.0..- Honey. you're in the shot.\N- Here she comes.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:39.38.0:14:41.51.Default..0.0.0..[dad] {\i1}Get out of the way.{\i0}\N{\i1}Sorry. thank you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:14:41.59.0:14:43.55.Default..0.0.0..[camcorder whirring]
Dialogue: 0.0:14:43.63.0:14:45.39.Default..0.0.0..[dad] {\i1}Oh. doesn't she look beautiful?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:14:45.47.0:14:47.39.Default..0.0.0..[bishop] …Holy Spirit.\NPeace be with you.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:50.72.0:14:53.31.Default..0.0.0..Heather Elizabeth Smurl.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:53.39.0:14:54.89.Default..0.0.0..Heather Elizabeth Smurl.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:55.44.0:14:57.56.Default..0.0.0..be sealed with the gift\Nof the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:58.19.0:14:59.15.Default..0.0.0..Amen.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:59.23.0:15:00.11.Default..0.0.0..Peace be with you.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:00.19.0:15:01.86.Default..0.0.0..[camcorder whirring]
Dialogue: 0.0:15:02.90.0:15:03.90.Default..0.0.0..[dad] {\i1}There she is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:15:06.41.0:15:07.95.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}She's confirmed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:15:08.03.0:15:09.66.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- You did it. honey.{\i0}\N- [crackle]
Dialogue: 0.0:15:12.41.0:15:14.75.Default..0.0.0..- Hey. girls! Who wants dinner?\N- We do!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:14.83.0:15:17.21.Default..0.0.0..- Come on! Get inside. then!\N- I'm super hungry!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:17.29.0:15:20.34.Default..0.0.0..Hurry. hurry! Chop. chop. chop!\NIt's getting cold!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:20.42.0:15:23.17.Default..0.0.0..…to call.\NYes. it was a beautiful ceremony.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:23.97.0:15:25.97.Default..0.0.0..- John. stop!\N- Oh. honey!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:26.05.0:15:28.35.Default..0.0.0..You know how much I love your dips!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:28.85.0:15:30.39.Default..0.0.0..- Ah! I love it!\N- Ugh…
Dialogue: 0.0:15:33.85.0:15:35.31.Default..0.0.0..- Hold on…\N- Where should I put the salad?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:35.39.0:15:36.44.Default..0.0.0..[grandpa] Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:37.40.0:15:38.06.Default..0.0.0..[child giggles]
Dialogue: 0.0:15:38.15.0:15:40.11.Default..0.0.0..[Heather] Grandma?\NWhere do you want the salad?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:40.40.0:15:41.61.Default..0.0.0..[screams. laughter]
Dialogue: 0.0:15:41.69.0:15:43.53.Default..0.0.0..You two think you're so funny!
Dialogue: 0.0:15:43.61.0:15:46.70.Default..0.0.0..Hey. what's all this noise? [laughs]
Dialogue: 0.0:15:46.78.0:15:48.87.Default..0.0.0..- Sorry. that was the girls.\N- Hey. no running in the house. girls.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:49.32.0:15:53.12.Default..0.0.0..[dad] {\i1}Okay. Round up. round up.{\i0}\N{\i1}What do we have here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:15:53.20.0:15:56.12.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- It's taller than I am!{\i0}\N- [family chuckling]
Dialogue: 0.0:15:56.21.0:15:57.04.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Oh. my gosh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:15:57.12.0:15:59.00.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}I didn't get anything for my confirmation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:15:59.08.0:16:01.54.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- Dawn…{\i0}\N{\i1}- I thought we got you that nice brooch?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:16:01.63.0:16:03.34.Default..0.0.0..- [grandpa] {\i1}Yeah.{\i0}\N{\i1}- Oh. yeah…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:16:03.42.0:16:04.80.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Yeah. there was that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:16:04.88.0:16:06.55.Default..0.0.0..- [grandpa] {\i1}Go on. open it.{\i0}\N{\i1}- Okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:16:07.93.0:16:09.93.Default..0.0.0..[dad mimics drum roll]
Dialogue: 0.0:16:10.93.0:16:12.22.Default..0.0.0..[family laughing]
Dialogue: 0.0:16:16.56.0:16:17.69.Default..0.0.0..- It's a mirror.\N- [dog barks]
Dialogue: 0.0:16:19.40.0:16:20.98.Default..0.0.0..[barking continues]
Dialogue: 0.0:16:21.06.0:16:22.23.Default..0.0.0..It's got a crack.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:22.32.0:16:23.78.Default..0.0.0..- [dad] Oh. Heather…\N- [grandma] Oh. sweetie.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:23.86.0:16:25.82.Default..0.0.0..Grandpa can fix the glass.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:25.90.0:16:28.82.Default..0.0.0..We found it at the swap meet.\Nover in Bucks County.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:28.91.0:16:30.24.Default..0.0.0..- [dad] Simon. hush!\N- You did?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:30.32.0:16:31.45.Default..0.0.0..[barking continues]
Dialogue: 0.0:16:31.53.0:16:33.24.Default..0.0.0..- [Simon panting]\N- Hey…
Dialogue: 0.0:16:34.87.0:16:36.45.Default..0.0.0..- I love it.\N- [relieved laughter]
Dialogue: 0.0:16:36.54.0:16:37.96.Default..0.0.0..Thanks. Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:38.04.0:16:40.38.Default..0.0.0..- Oh. honey. you're welcome.\N- Thanks. Gran.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:40.46.0:16:42.38.Default..0.0.0..Oh. sweetheart!
Dialogue: 0.0:16:42.96.0:16:45.55.Default..0.0.0..- Mom. I hope it wasn't too much.\N- Oh. don't worry.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:45.63.0:16:49.38.Default..0.0.0..The man couldn't get it back in his truck.\Nso he gave us a little deal.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:50.05.0:16:52.22.Default..0.0.0..I think it was just waiting for us.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:52.30.0:16:53.76.Default..0.0.0..We know the bathroom gets crowded.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:53.85.0:16:55.89.Default..0.0.0..You can put it in your room.\Nand you don't have to share with anyone.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:55.97.0:16:57.06.Default..0.0.0..- That's a good idea.\N- [Dawn] That is not going
Dialogue: 0.0:16:57.14.0:16:58.23.Default..0.0.0..- in our bedroom.\N- [mom] Well. I…
Dialogue: 0.0:16:58.31.0:16:59.69.Default..0.0.0..- [Dawn] Are you serious?\N- …think it's lovely…
Dialogue: 0.0:16:59.77.0:17:00.94.Default..0.0.0..…and very thoughtful.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:01.02.0:17:02.23.Default..0.0.0..- [dad] No more queues.\N- [Simon barks]
Dialogue: 0.0:17:02.31.0:17:06.03.Default..0.0.0..Doesn't the one up at the top\Nlook just like you when you were a baby?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:06.11.0:17:07.78.Default..0.0.0..[laughs] Oh. yeah. definitely.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:07.86.0:17:08.99.Default..0.0.0..- I can see that.\N- [bang]
Dialogue: 0.0:17:09.07.0:17:10.11.Default..0.0.0..Ow!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:10.61.0:17:11.99.Default..0.0.0..- [mom] Heather!\N- My foot slipped.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:12.07.0:17:13.53.Default..0.0.0..[mom] It did not. I saw that.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:13.62.0:17:15.16.Default..0.0.0..- Okay. seriously. though.\N- Dawn's foot got in the way.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:15.24.0:17:16.66.Default..0.0.0..Not now. Right…
Dialogue: 0.0:17:16.75.0:17:18.20.Default..0.0.0..That resemblance is crazy.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:18.83.0:17:20.71.Default..0.0.0..- You've got the bangs and everything.\N- Who wants cake?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:20.79.0:17:22.79.Default..0.0.0..- [girls] I do! I do! I do!\N- [barking continues]
Dialogue: 0.0:17:25.67.0:17:27.84.Default..0.0.0..- [mom] Okay!\N- [dad ooh-ing]
Dialogue: 0.0:17:27.92.0:17:30.26.Default..0.0.0..- [mom] Come on. There we go!\N- [dad] There we go!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:30.76.0:17:32.26.Default..0.0.0..[Dawn] It looks so good.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:32.34.0:17:33.85.Default..0.0.0..[dad mimics fanfare]
Dialogue: 0.0:17:33.93.0:17:35.93.Default..0.0.0..[dad] Confirmation cake!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:36.81.0:17:39.56.Default..0.0.0..- [mom] {\i1}Congratulations. sweetheart.{\i0}\N{\i1}- Thank you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:17:39.64.0:17:40.89.Default..0.0.0..I definitely didn't get a cake.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:40.98.0:17:42.23.Default..0.0.0..- Don't forget to make a wish.\N- [barking]
Dialogue: 0.0:17:42.31.0:17:43.23.Default..0.0.0..Simon. hush!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:43.31.0:17:44.40.Default..0.0.0..[girl] Simon wants some cake. too.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:44.48.0:17:45.82.Default..0.0.0..Here we go!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:45.90.0:17:46.98.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Ready?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:17:47.57.0:17:48.82.Default..0.0.0..[deep inhale]
Dialogue: 0.0:17:49.86.0:17:51.32.Default..0.0.0..Hey. what? She blew out my candles.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:51.40.0:17:53.16.Default..0.0.0..- Who?\N- Dawn!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:53.24.0:17:54.99.Default..0.0.0..- No. I didn't!\N- You did!
Dialogue: 0.0:17:55.07.0:17:56.87.Default..0.0.0..- [Dawn] No. I didn't!\N- [grandma] Get some light on.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:56.95.0:17:58.70.Default..0.0.0..- [dad] It's all right.\N- I actually didn't blow them out.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:58.79.0:18:00.41.Default..0.0.0..[dad] It's okay. guys.\NCome on. let's have a bit of peace.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:00.50.0:18:01.25.Default..0.0.0..She did.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:01.50.0:18:02.67.Default..0.0.0..[all screaming]
Dialogue: 0.0:18:02.75.0:18:03.67.Default..0.0.0..[Dawn] Oh. my God!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:03.75.0:18:05.04.Default..0.0.0..[grandma] Heather! Oh. my God!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:05.13.0:18:07.05.Default..0.0.0..[girl] Heather! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:07.13.0:18:08.25.Default..0.0.0..[mom] It's okay. What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:08.34.0:18:11.26.Default..0.0.0..[Dawn] Oh. my God.\NDad? That is a lot of blood.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:11.34.0:18:12.43.Default..0.0.0..[dad] Did it hit you?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:12.51.0:18:14.64.Default..0.0.0..Oh. my God. are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:14.72.0:18:16.14.Default..0.0.0..[Dawn] Hey. it's okay. it's okay.\NJust squeeze my hand.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:16.22.0:18:18.85.Default..0.0.0..- It's okay. It's okay.\N- I'll go and get the first aid kit!
Dialogue: 0.0:18:43.04.0:18:47.46.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}[discordant choir vocalizing]
Dialogue: 0.0:18:54.63.0:18:56.09.Default..0.0.0..[vocalizing stops]
Dialogue: 0.0:18:58.76.0:19:00.10.Default..0.0.0..[bell tolls]
Dialogue: 0.0:19:00.18.0:19:03.85.Default..0.0.0..[Ed] The young occupants of the apartment\Nthought they were speaking to the spirit
Dialogue: 0.0:19:03.94.0:19:06.15.Default..0.0.0..of a little girl named Annabelle Mullins.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:06.23.0:19:09.61.Default..0.0.0..But in reality. they were communing\Nwith an inhuman spirit.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:09.90.0:19:11.07.Default..0.0.0..A demon.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:11.15.0:19:13.36.Default..0.0.0..It played on their sympathies.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:13.44.0:19:15.45.Default..0.0.0..It played on their compassion.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:15.99.0:19:19.83.Default..0.0.0..It then asked for permission\Nto enter the doll as its vessel.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:19.91.0:19:22.04.Default..0.0.0..a conduit into our world.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:22.12.0:19:24.46.Default..0.0.0..We've encountered hundreds\Nof items like Annabelle.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:25.54.0:19:28.71.Default..0.0.0..- Cursed objects. totems…\N- [projector clicks]
Dialogue: 0.0:19:28.79.0:19:32.17.Default..0.0.0..…and over the years. we've found that\Nthe best solution was to collect them.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:32.26.0:19:34.22.Default..0.0.0..It's like taking guns off the streets.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:34.30.0:19:36.63.Default..0.0.0..- [clicks]\N- Hang on. sorry.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:36.72.0:19:38.18.Default..0.0.0..[projector whirs. clicks]
Dialogue: 0.0:19:40.14.0:19:41.31.Default..0.0.0..You know what?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:41.39.0:19:42.81.Default..0.0.0..Will one of you hit the lights?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:43.93.0:19:45.10.Default..0.0.0..[groans]
Dialogue: 0.0:19:46.60.0:19:47.85.Default..0.0.0..[Ed] All right.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:48.56.0:19:50.44.Default..0.0.0..Okay. Uh. any questions?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:52.03.0:19:53.03.Default..0.0.0..Yes?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:53.57.0:19:56.11.Default..0.0.0..So. you guys were\Nkind of like {\i1}The Ghostbusters?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:19:56.20.0:19:59.03.Default..0.0.0..Uh. no. We didn't… bust ghosts.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:59.12.0:20:01.16.Default..0.0.0..But we did see the movie. [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0.0:20:01.45.0:20:03.66.Default..0.0.0..Wait! So. you never got slimed?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:03.75.0:20:05.04.Default..0.0.0..- [laughs]\N- Please…
Dialogue: 0.0:20:05.75.0:20:07.37.Default..0.0.0..Any serious questions?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:08.17.0:20:09.04.Default..0.0.0..Yes?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:09.13.0:20:10.46.Default..0.0.0..Why did you stop?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:11.38.0:20:12.34.Default..0.0.0..We haven't stopped.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:12.42.0:20:14.59.Default..0.0.0..We're travelling. we're doing lectures.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:14.67.0:20:16.01.Default..0.0.0..We may even write a book.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:16.55.0:20:18.84.Default..0.0.0..But you're not taking cases anymore.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:18.93.0:20:21.43.Default..0.0.0..Well. we've decided to. um.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:21.76.0:20:23.51.Default..0.0.0..to focus on other parts of our life.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:23.60.0:20:24.56.Default..0.0.0..Mm.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:24.64.0:20:26.06.Default..0.0.0..[student] Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:26.68.0:20:28.98.Default..0.0.0..- "Who ya gonna call?"\N- [scattered laughter]
Dialogue: 0.0:20:30.36.0:20:31.56.Default..0.0.0..[door opens]
Dialogue: 0.0:20:32.19.0:20:34.53.Default..0.0.0..- Well… thank you.\N- [door slams]
Dialogue: 0.0:20:40.37.0:20:42.20.Default..0.0.0..[Ed] Our entire life's work…
Dialogue: 0.0:20:42.28.0:20:45.54.Default..0.0.0..It's like some sort of\N{\i1}Saturday Night Live {\i0}skit.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:45.62.0:20:47.25.Default..0.0.0..- [Judy snickers]\N- Wha-- It's not funny!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:47.33.0:20:49.33.Default..0.0.0..Dad. it wasn't that bad!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:49.42.0:20:51.04.Default..0.0.0..[Ed sighs]
Dialogue: 0.0:20:51.13.0:20:55.09.Default..0.0.0..Hon. I think you're not seeing\Nthe forest for the trees.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:55.17.0:20:56.01.Default..0.0.0..[sighs]
Dialogue: 0.0:20:56.09.0:20:57.92.Default..0.0.0..Or the ghosts for the graveyard.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:58.01.0:20:59.51.Default..0.0.0..Oh. great.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:00.68.0:21:02.01.Default..0.0.0..People weren't even listening. though.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:02.10.0:21:04.22.Default..0.0.0..[stammers]\NThey're not even engaged anymore.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:04.31.0:21:07.18.Default..0.0.0..It's like they're just all\Nwaiting for a punchline.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:08.52.0:21:10.27.Default..0.0.0..They're just having fun.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:11.23.0:21:12.31.Default..0.0.0..I guess.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:13.77.0:21:15.65.Default..0.0.0..When they asked why you guys quit.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:15.73.0:21:17.78.Default..0.0.0..why didn't you just say.\N'cause of your heart?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:19.86.0:21:22.24.Default..0.0.0..Because that's what an old man would say.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:23.57.0:21:26.74.Default..0.0.0..Besides. it-it's more a hiatus\Nthan retirement.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:27.29.0:21:29.75.Default..0.0.0..It's… It's just until\Nthe doc clears me again.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:29.83.0:21:30.83.Default..0.0.0..Right. hon?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:34.09.0:21:37.34.Default..0.0.0..Well. in the meantime.\Nwe have your birthday coming up.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:37.42.0:21:39.80.Default..0.0.0..- Mm-hmm. [chuckles]\N- And I was thinking
Dialogue: 0.0:21:39.88.0:21:41.34.Default..0.0.0..of bringing Tony to the party.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:41.43.0:21:42.09.Default..0.0.0..Who's Tony?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:42.18.0:21:44.26.Default..0.0.0..Dad! We've been dating for six months.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:44.35.0:21:45.72.Default..0.0.0..Oh. that Tony.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:45.81.0:21:47.64.Default..0.0.0..[scoffs] You're not funny.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:47.72.0:21:50.31.Default..0.0.0..Of course. sweetheart. We love him.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:51.39.0:21:52.94.Default..0.0.0..- We do?\N- Ed.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:53.44.0:21:54.52.Default..0.0.0..- We do.\N- [waitress] You guys ready?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:54.61.0:21:55.82.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:55.90.0:21:58.32.Default..0.0.0..I'll have the linguine with clams. please.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:58.40.0:22:00.11.Default..0.0.0..- [waitress] Yeah. great choice.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:01.20.0:22:02.03.Default..0.0.0..Who's next?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:04.24.0:22:05.74.Default..0.0.0..Uh. yeah. I can do it.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:05.83.0:22:06.95.Default..0.0.0..Um…
Dialogue: 0.0:22:08.12.0:22:10.62.Default..0.0.0..Boy. you got\Na lot of good stuff here. Um…
Dialogue: 0.0:22:11.12.0:22:13.42.Default..0.0.0..[fading] I'm on\Na bit of a heart healthy diet…
Dialogue: 0.0:22:13.50.0:22:15.50.Default..0.0.0..[faint. sinister whispering]
Dialogue: 0.0:22:18.71.0:22:20.51.Default..0.0.0..[Judy whispering] ♪ {\i1}…found it{\i0}\N{\i1}Not a penny was there in it {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:22:20.59.0:22:21.92.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Only ribbon 'round it {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:22:24.05.0:22:26.64.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Not a penny was there in it{\i0}\N{\i1}Only ribbon 'round it {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:22:26.72.0:22:29.39.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Lucy Locket lost her pocket{\i0}\N{\i1}Kitty Fisher found it {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:22:29.47.0:22:32.02.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Not a penny was there in it{\i0}\N{\i1}Only ribbon 'round it {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:22:32.10.0:22:35.10.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Lucy Locket lost her pocket{\i0}\N{\i1}Kitty Fisher found it {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:22:36.48.0:22:38.90.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Lucy Locket lost her pocket{\i0}\N{\i1}Kitty Fisher found it {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:22:38.98.0:22:41.36.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Not a penny was there in it{\i0}\N{\i1}Only ribbon 'round it {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:22:41.44.0:22:42.86.Default..0.0.0..♪{\i1} You're not there {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:22:42.95.0:22:44.53.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Lucy Locket lost her pocket-- {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:22:44.61.0:22:46.03.Default..0.0.0..[trembling breath]
Dialogue: 0.0:22:46.12.0:22:47.70.Default..0.0.0..- [Ed] Grilled steak slices…\N- [panting]
Dialogue: 0.0:22:47.78.0:22:49.95.Default..0.0.0..…over mixed greens. Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:50.04.0:22:53.08.Default..0.0.0..Can I get that but with chicken?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:53.16.0:22:53.96.Default..0.0.0..[waitress] Sure.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:54.83.0:22:55.96.Default..0.0.0..Dressing on the side?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:56.83.0:22:57.63.Default..0.0.0..[sighs]
Dialogue: 0.0:22:59.21.0:23:00.84.Default..0.0.0..- [gasps]\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 0.0:23:03.05.0:23:03.84.Default..0.0.0..Lorraine?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:05.59.0:23:07.51.Default..0.0.0..[waitress] Ma'am? You okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:08.14.0:23:08.89.Default..0.0.0..Yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:09.43.0:23:10.56.Default..0.0.0..Yes. I'm-- I'm--
Dialogue: 0.0:23:10.64.0:23:12.93.Default..0.0.0..I'm fine. I thought--\NI thought I saw something.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:13.02.0:23:14.44.Default..0.0.0..[stammering] I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:15.90.0:23:17.02.Default..0.0.0..[waitress] Did you make up your mind?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:18.94.0:23:20.82.Default..0.0.0..- Sorry. What?\N- The lasagna.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:21.36.0:23:22.61.Default..0.0.0..She loves the lasagna.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:23.03.0:23:23.99.Default..0.0.0..Right. sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:25.20.0:23:26.70.Default..0.0.0..[waitress] Yeah. great choice. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:26.78.0:23:27.49.Default..0.0.0..Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:28.16.0:23:29.45.Default..0.0.0..Nice. It's coming right up.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:29.87.0:23:30.87.Default..0.0.0..You two all right?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:32.50.0:23:33.62.Default..0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:39.17.0:23:40.67.Default..0.0.0..Wish I could have lasagna.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:00.69.0:24:01.77.Default..0.0.0..[toy] {\i1}Mommy. Mommy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:24:01.86.0:24:03.69.Default..0.0.0..[whirring]
Dialogue: 0.0:24:06.74.0:24:07.78.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Mommy. Mommy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:24:08.74.0:24:10.58.Default..0.0.0..What are you doing in here?
Dialogue: 0.0:24:12.58.0:24:13.24.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Mom--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:24:14.95.0:24:15.71.Default..0.0.0..[sighs]
Dialogue: 0.0:24:28.01.0:24:32.51.Default..0.0.0..[washer spinning. rattling]
Dialogue: 0.0:24:38.48.0:24:39.77.Default..0.0.0..[rattling stops]
Dialogue: 0.0:24:41.52.0:24:43.15.Default..0.0.0..- [eerie voice whispers] {\i1}Janet…{\i0}\N- [Janet gasps]
Dialogue: 0.0:25:05.25.0:25:07.26.Default..0.0.0..[low rumbling]
Dialogue: 0.0:25:09.84.0:25:13.01.Default..0.0.0..[nervous breathing]
Dialogue: 0.0:25:14.93.0:25:16.72.Default..0.0.0..- [clicks]\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 0.0:25:19.19.0:25:24.57.Default..0.0.0..- [thud]\N- [washer rumbling]
Dialogue: 0.0:25:31.07.0:25:32.32.Default..0.0.0..- [mom] No.\N- [girls giggling]
Dialogue: 0.0:25:32.41.0:25:33.57.Default..0.0.0..No. that's what Margie was saying.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:33.66.0:25:36.08.Default..0.0.0..Wait! We're gonna be late\Nfor Mister Pinky Pop's birthday party.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:36.16.0:25:39.08.Default..0.0.0..I knew that they were having problems.\NI just didn't know it was that bad.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:39.16.0:25:40.71.Default..0.0.0..[Carin] Hurry up. Shannon!
Dialogue: 0.0:25:40.79.0:25:42.33.Default..0.0.0..- [girls giggling]\N- He's gonna be
Dialogue: 0.0:25:42.42.0:25:44.25.Default..0.0.0..- really mad if you're late.\N- What a shame.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:44.34.0:25:45.92.Default..0.0.0..[girls giggling]
Dialogue: 0.0:25:46.71.0:25:47.92.Default..0.0.0..[Carin] Come on!
Dialogue: 0.0:25:48.01.0:25:49.55.Default..0.0.0..[indistinct phone chatter]
Dialogue: 0.0:25:49.63.0:25:50.47.Default..0.0.0..No.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:50.55.0:25:51.80.Default..0.0.0..[creak]
Dialogue: 0.0:25:51.88.0:25:54.14.Default..0.0.0..Girls. stop it!
Dialogue: 0.0:25:55.01.0:25:57.81.Default..0.0.0..[phone chatter continues]
Dialogue: 0.0:26:04.31.0:26:04.98.Default..0.0.0..No.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:06.07.0:26:07.61.Default..0.0.0..I don't think that that's true.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:10.61.0:26:11.99.Default..0.0.0..Alice wouldn't want that.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:12.82.0:26:14.45.Default..0.0.0..Known her since we were in high school.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:15.95.0:26:16.78.Default..0.0.0..No.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:17.24.0:26:18.95.Default..0.0.0..She didn't say that. no.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:19.04.0:26:20.79.Default..0.0.0..[gasps] Girls!
Dialogue: 0.0:26:24.13.0:26:26.17.Default..0.0.0..Girls. you come outta there. right now!
Dialogue: 0.0:26:27.55.0:26:29.34.Default..0.0.0..[girls giggling]
Dialogue: 0.0:26:31.67.0:26:33.13.Default..0.0.0..[female caller] {\i1}Janet. are you there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:26:35.68.0:26:36.85.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Did I lose ya?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:26:41.64.0:26:42.73.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Janet?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:26:48.98.0:26:50.15.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Hello?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:26:50.86.0:26:51.74.Default..0.0.0..[gasps]
Dialogue: 0.0:26:53.49.0:26:54.36.Default..0.0.0..[gasps]
Dialogue: 0.0:26:58.62.0:27:00.16.Default..0.0.0..[gasping]
Dialogue: 0.0:27:04.42.0:27:05.42.Default..0.0.0..[Carin] Here you go.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:05.50.0:27:07.46.Default..0.0.0..You want some soup?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:09.13.0:27:10.96.Default..0.0.0..'Kay. Susie. I'm gonna\Nmake you some soup.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:11.05.0:27:13.01.Default..0.0.0..and I'll be right back with you.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:13.67.0:27:14.43.Default..0.0.0.."Okay!"
Dialogue: 0.0:27:15.55.0:27:16.64.Default..0.0.0..[Shannon] You can.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:16.72.0:27:19.18.Default..0.0.0..So. here. it says "welcome." Oh.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:19.26.0:27:20.64.Default..0.0.0..[Carin] Here's corn.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:20.72.0:27:22.98.Default..0.0.0..Can you make that carrot soup\Nthat we like?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:23.06.0:27:24.14.Default..0.0.0..[Shannon] Of course!
Dialogue: 0.0:27:24.23.0:27:25.94.Default..0.0.0..- And when do you want this?\N- Okay. perfect!
Dialogue: 0.0:27:26.02.0:27:27.94.Default..0.0.0..Okay. made your soup for you. Susie.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:32.53.0:27:33.61.Default..0.0.0..Where's Susie?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:36.74.0:27:38.74.Default..0.0.0..[footsteps]
Dialogue: 0.0:27:40.99.0:27:41.99.Default..0.0.0..[Susie] {\i1}Mommy. Mommy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:27:44.54.0:27:45.66.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Mommy. Mommy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:27:49.96.0:27:50.96.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Mommy. Mommy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:27:51.59.0:27:53.13.Default..0.0.0..How did you get in here. Susie?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:55.34.0:27:57.84.Default..0.0.0..[whirring]
Dialogue: 0.0:27:58.34.0:28:00.22.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Mommy! Mommy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:28:16.82.0:28:18.74.Default..0.0.0..[gasping]
Dialogue: 0.0:28:21.74.0:28:22.95.Default..0.0.0..[evil chuckle]
Dialogue: 0.0:28:23.37.0:28:25.04.Default..0.0.0..[screams]
Dialogue: 0.0:28:25.12.0:28:26.33.Default..0.0.0..Mommy!
Dialogue: 0.0:28:27.21.0:28:28.71.Default..0.0.0..[low echoing]
Dialogue: 0.0:28:34.92.0:28:35.76.Default..0.0.0..[handbrake creaks]
Dialogue: 0.0:28:39.22.0:28:40.97.Default..0.0.0..[train whistle blows in distance]
Dialogue: 0.0:28:43.85.0:28:45.81.Default..0.0.0..- [Simon barking]\N- Hey. hey. hey…
Dialogue: 0.0:28:46.60.0:28:48.19.Default..0.0.0..- Come here. come here!\N- [Shannon] She stole my doll.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:48.27.0:28:49.65.Default..0.0.0..- You have a good day?\N- [Shannon] She stole Susie!
Dialogue: 0.0:28:49.73.0:28:50.69.Default..0.0.0..You been a good boy?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:50.77.0:28:51.77.Default..0.0.0..Good boy.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:52.15.0:28:53.82.Default..0.0.0..- Hey. Dad. What are you watching?\N- Hi. son.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:53.90.0:28:56.03.Default..0.0.0..- It's not very good.\N- Mommy! Mom. she stole my doll!
Dialogue: 0.0:28:56.11.0:28:57.86.Default..0.0.0..- Hello. everyone!\N- She stole Susie!
Dialogue: 0.0:28:57.95.0:28:59.24.Default..0.0.0..Hi. sweetie.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:59.86.0:29:02.66.Default..0.0.0..- Okay.\N- Could you get the cutlery out over there?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:02.74.0:29:04.62.Default..0.0.0..Daddy. no one believes me!
Dialogue: 0.0:29:04.70.0:29:05.37.Default..0.0.0..- [dad] What?\N- [Dawn] Sorry. Mom.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:05.45.0:29:06.75.Default..0.0.0..- [Carin] She's speaking nonsense!\N- Believes you what?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:06.83.0:29:07.66.Default..0.0.0..[Shannon] I'm not!
Dialogue: 0.0:29:08.08.0:29:10.17.Default..0.0.0..[dad] I'll believe you.\NYou just tell me what this is about.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:10.25.0:29:12.17.Default..0.0.0..- I was playing in Dawn's room…\N- Thank you for the floodlights.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:12.25.0:29:14.88.Default..0.0.0..- …with Susie. and then--\N- Shannon! She thinks she saw…
Dialogue: 0.0:29:14.96.0:29:16.67.Default..0.0.0..- No one believes me. Granddad!\N- …an old woman in Dawn's room.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:16.76.0:29:17.84.Default..0.0.0..- [grandpa] Yeah. I believe you!\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:17.92.0:29:19.84.Default..0.0.0..- That's everything. Sit down.\N- An old lady took Susie.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:19.93.0:29:22.26.Default..0.0.0..- I was at the store.\N- Simon believes you.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:22.34.0:29:23.51.Default..0.0.0..Simon believes…
Dialogue: 0.0:29:23.60.0:29:25.56.Default..0.0.0..- Grandma. stop scaring Carin.\N- Come on. sit down.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:25.64.0:29:27.85.Default..0.0.0..[dad] All right. everyone.\NI am hungry. Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:27.93.0:29:29.94.Default..0.0.0..- Why does no one believe me?\N- I'll believe you.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:30.02.0:29:31.44.Default..0.0.0..You can tell me all about it after dinner.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:31.52.0:29:32.52.Default..0.0.0..[mom] Please sit down. sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:32.61.0:29:33.73.Default..0.0.0..- [grandpa] All right.\N- [grandma] Squeeze in. Carin.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:33.81.0:29:35.52.Default..0.0.0..- Come on. sit down.\N- Maybe it was Grandma.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:35.61.0:29:36.73.Default..0.0.0..All right!
Dialogue: 0.0:29:37.28.0:29:38.32.Default..0.0.0..Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:40.28.0:29:41.91.Default..0.0.0..For what we're about to receive.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:41.99.0:29:44.49.Default..0.0.0..may the Lord make us truly thankful.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:44.99.0:29:45.66.Default..0.0.0..- Amen.\N- Amen.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:45.74.0:29:46.58.Default..0.0.0..- Amen.\N- Amen.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:47.58.0:29:48.54.Default..0.0.0..All right. let's eat.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:48.62.0:29:50.37.Default..0.0.0..- This looks great!\N- I want some meatballs!
Dialogue: 0.0:29:51.00.0:29:52.71.Default..0.0.0..[voice fading] Meatballs are my favorite.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:53.92.0:29:55.92.Default..0.0.0..[pop music playing softly]
Dialogue: 0.0:30:10.77.0:30:13.48.Default..0.0.0..- It's so weird.\N- I know you are.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:14.36.0:30:15.48.Default..0.0.0..[scoffs]
Dialogue: 0.0:30:16.36.0:30:18.15.Default..0.0.0..Wait. what's weird?
Dialogue: 0.0:30:20.49.0:30:21.36.Default..0.0.0..The mirror.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:22.20.0:30:23.53.Default..0.0.0..Ugh. I know.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:24.16.0:30:26.91.Default..0.0.0..It's like those creepy-looking\Nbabies are always watching me.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:26.99.0:30:29.91.Default..0.0.0..Well. babies are perverts.\NBabies are gross.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:31.16.0:30:32.16.Default..0.0.0..Seriously.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:32.25.0:30:33.54.Default..0.0.0..[snickers]
Dialogue: 0.0:30:34.08.0:30:36.00.Default..0.0.0..[chuckling]
Dialogue: 0.0:30:36.09.0:30:39.00.Default..0.0.0.."The one in the middle\Nlooks just like you. Heather."
Dialogue: 0.0:30:39.09.0:30:40.42.Default..0.0.0..[laughs]
Dialogue: 0.0:30:40.51.0:30:43.97.Default..0.0.0..That was so funny. but that's a lie.\NYou were a much uglier baby.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:44.05.0:30:44.84.Default..0.0.0..Jeez. thanks.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:45.14.0:30:48.76.Default..0.0.0..You know. you should've seen the cards\NMom and Dad got in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:49.72.0:30:52.27.Default..0.0.0.."Janet. we're so sorry\Nyour daughter came out
Dialogue: 0.0:30:52.35.0:30:53.94.Default..0.0.0..looking like that guy Sloth from {\i1}Goonies."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:30:54.23.0:30:55.35.Default..0.0.0..You're an asshole!
Dialogue: 0.0:30:55.44.0:30:57.11.Default..0.0.0..[laughs]
Dialogue: 0.0:31:07.20.0:31:08.03.Default..0.0.0..You know.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:09.12.0:31:10.66.Default..0.0.0..it's trash day tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:17.96.0:31:19.21.Default..0.0.0..[grunting]
Dialogue: 0.0:31:22.38.0:31:23.47.Default..0.0.0..[whispering] Ow.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:23.97.0:31:25.97.Default..0.0.0..[both grunting. panting]
Dialogue: 0.0:31:39.94.0:31:41.19.Default..0.0.0..[Heather] Let's take it 'round the bend.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:41.28.0:31:42.69.Default..0.0.0..[both panting]
Dialogue: 0.0:31:43.57.0:31:45.11.Default..0.0.0..[grunts]
Dialogue: 0.0:31:45.20.0:31:47.24.Default..0.0.0..[Dawn] Oh. my God. that was so heavy!
Dialogue: 0.0:31:47.78.0:31:49.20.Default..0.0.0..[Heather] What if Grandma asks about it?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:49.87.0:31:53.91.Default..0.0.0..[Dawn] It was the twins. They did it.\NThey broke it. We just took it outside.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:54.00.0:31:55.12.Default..0.0.0..[Heather. whispering] Good idea.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:55.83.0:31:57.37.Default..0.0.0..[Dawn] I know. I'm a genius.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:57.46.0:31:59.84.Default..0.0.0..[crackling]
Dialogue: 0.0:31:59.92.0:32:02.76.Default..0.0.0..[rumbling]
Dialogue: 0.0:32:04.30.0:32:05.59.Default..0.0.0..[dad] Morning. everyone. Carin!
Dialogue: 0.0:32:05.67.0:32:07.09.Default..0.0.0..Get down from there. What's she doing?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:07.18.0:32:08.80.Default..0.0.0..- Stay. Simon. stay. Simon. go!\N- Carin. come on down.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:09.35.0:32:11.43.Default..0.0.0..Carin. come on now. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:11.51.0:32:13.10.Default..0.0.0..- Making me some sandwiches?\N- Honey.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:13.18.0:32:14.56.Default..0.0.0..I am making the girls some sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:14.64.0:32:16.48.Default..0.0.0..- What about my lunch?\N- I've got your lunch.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:16.56.0:32:18.06.Default..0.0.0.."Win a family vacation to Florida."
Dialogue: 0.0:32:18.15.0:32:20.31.Default..0.0.0..- Oh. my gosh!\N- How cool would that be?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:20.40.0:32:21.07.Default..0.0.0..Pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:21.15.0:32:24.23.Default..0.0.0..- You really stink. Simon.\N- He's farting all the time. now.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:24.32.0:32:25.28.Default..0.0.0..[grandpa] That's the bacon.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:25.36.0:32:26.86.Default..0.0.0..- [Carin] I don't really…\N- No!
Dialogue: 0.0:32:26.95.0:32:29.11.Default..0.0.0..Don't slap me with cheese.\NYou know what happened.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:29.20.0:32:30.70.Default..0.0.0..the last time you slapped me with cheese?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:30.78.0:32:32.95.Default..0.0.0..- What? [laughs]\N- I was down on my knees. Mm-mm!
Dialogue: 0.0:32:38.25.0:32:40.00.Default..0.0.0..[brakes squeal]
Dialogue: 0.0:32:41.96.0:32:42.75.Default..0.0.0..I got it.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:48.05.0:32:49.76.Default..0.0.0..- Get the other end of this?\N- Yep.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:55.22.0:32:57.35.Default..0.0.0..- You ready?\N- It'll fit.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:00.85.0:33:02.23.Default..0.0.0..[cutlery clinking]
Dialogue: 0.0:33:02.31.0:33:04.36.Default..0.0.0..[Carin] Yeah. I don't own a piggy bank.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:04.44.0:33:06.03.Default..0.0.0..[Shannon] I don't have two dollars.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:07.70.0:33:09.74.Default..0.0.0..[Carin] I don't have one.\NIt's just a prank.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:09.82.0:33:11.82.Default..0.0.0..[family chattering indistinctly]
Dialogue: 0.0:33:13.70.0:33:15.83.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. maybe we'll have two dollars.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:15.91.0:33:16.79.Default..0.0.0..Four dollars!
Dialogue: 0.0:33:16.87.0:33:18.12.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. that would be good.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:18.50.0:33:20.37.Default..0.0.0..Well. you have a birthday coming up soon.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:27.13.0:33:29.88.Default..0.0.0..- [stomach gurgling]\N- [coughs. gags]
Dialogue: 0.0:33:29.97.0:33:31.51.Default..0.0.0..[Dawn gagging]
Dialogue: 0.0:33:31.59.0:33:32.51.Default..0.0.0..Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:33.10.0:33:34.47.Default..0.0.0..[grunts. coughs]
Dialogue: 0.0:33:34.56.0:33:35.81.Default..0.0.0..- Dawn?\N- Sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:35.89.0:33:37.68.Default..0.0.0..- [gags. coughs]\N- Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:38.35.0:33:39.31.Default..0.0.0..- [grandpa] Honey?\N- [dad] Come on.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:39.60.0:33:40.56.Default..0.0.0..- You okay. Dawn?\N- [Carin] Dawn?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:40.64.0:33:42.65.Default..0.0.0..- Mm! Mm…\N- [stomach gurgling]
Dialogue: 0.0:33:42.86.0:33:45.73.Default..0.0.0..- Dawn. can you breathe okay?\N- [coughing]
Dialogue: 0.0:33:45.82.0:33:47.61.Default..0.0.0..- Are you choking?\N- Are you choking. sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:48.36.0:33:51.03.Default..0.0.0..- [dad] Oh. God! Oh. Dawn!\N- [twins scream]
Dialogue: 0.0:33:52.36.0:33:53.91.Default..0.0.0..[dad] Honey. Oh. my gosh.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:53.99.0:33:55.95.Default..0.0.0..Oh. my God. no!
Dialogue: 0.0:33:56.03.0:33:57.83.Default..0.0.0..- [grandpa] You'll be okay.\N- [grandma] Oh. my God.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:57.91.0:33:59.12.Default..0.0.0..- [pained moan]\N- [family yelling]
Dialogue: 0.0:33:59.20.0:34:00.25.Default..0.0.0..[screaming]
Dialogue: 0.0:34:00.33.0:34:02.00.Default..0.0.0..- Oh. Dawn!\N- Oh. Dawny!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:02.46.0:34:03.46.Default..0.0.0..[mom] Oh. my God!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:03.54.0:34:05.50.Default..0.0.0..- [pained sobbing]\N- [dad] Dawn!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:07.67.0:34:09.13.Default..0.0.0..- [dad] It's okay.\N- [gasping]
Dialogue: 0.0:34:09.55.0:34:10.47.Default..0.0.0..What is that?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:10.55.0:34:12.34.Default..0.0.0..Is that glass? Did you swallow glass?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:12.93.0:34:14.43.Default..0.0.0..[mom] We've gotta get to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:14.51.0:34:15.55.Default..0.0.0..- Yes.\N- Go!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:15.97.0:34:16.93.Default..0.0.0..[grandpa] Get her to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:17.01.0:34:18.52.Default..0.0.0..God. Jack!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:18.60.0:34:20.27.Default..0.0.0..[twins clamoring]
Dialogue: 0.0:34:20.64.0:34:21.73.Default..0.0.0..[grandpa] It's gonna be all right.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:21.81.0:34:22.64.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. yeah. it will.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:22.73.0:34:23.81.Default..0.0.0..- It's gonna be okay.\N- [grandma] Sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:23.90.0:34:25.52.Default..0.0.0..come and sit down. sweetie.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:25.61.0:34:27.07.Default..0.0.0..- Heather. sweetheart.\N- [hyperventilating]
Dialogue: 0.0:34:27.15.0:34:28.32.Default..0.0.0..Come on.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:28.40.0:34:30.57.Default..0.0.0..[hissing]
Dialogue: 0.0:34:34.20.0:34:36.07.Default..0.0.0..[phone rings]
Dialogue: 0.0:34:37.03.0:34:37.79.Default..0.0.0..That bad?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:38.37.0:34:40.41.Default..0.0.0..- Higher than I'd like.\N- [groans softly]
Dialogue: 0.0:34:40.50.0:34:42.96.Default..0.0.0..You ever think about adding fish\Nto your diet?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:43.04.0:34:45.25.Default..0.0.0..I'm not really a fish guy. doc.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:45.33.0:34:46.34.Default..0.0.0..What about egg whites?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:46.79.0:34:47.63.Default..0.0.0..Egg what?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:53.26.0:34:54.26.Default..0.0.0..Ed…
Dialogue: 0.0:34:55.68.0:34:58.18.Default..0.0.0..I've known you a long time. Cut the crap.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:58.97.0:34:59.81.Default..0.0.0..Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:59.89.0:35:02.06.Default..0.0.0..You can't have another heart attack.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:07.90.0:35:08.90.Default..0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:09.65.0:35:11.65.Default..0.0.0..["Love Has Me By The Hand"\Nby Spanky Wilson playing]
Dialogue: 0.0:35:13.78.0:35:18.83.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}♪ Love has me by the hand{\i0}\N{\i1}And I will follow ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:35:18.91.0:35:20.08.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine] Hannah… Out. out!
Dialogue: 0.0:35:20.16.0:35:21.20.Default..0.0.0..- Out. out. out!\N- [chicken clucking]
Dialogue: 0.0:35:22.12.0:35:23.83.Default..0.0.0..- Hi. it's good to see you.\N- How are you?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:23.91.0:35:25.25.Default..0.0.0..Lorraine. good to see you.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:25.33.0:35:28.50.Default..0.0.0..Look. help yourself to the hors d'oeuvres.\NI'll be right out.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:28.59.0:35:30.59.Default..0.0.0..[music continues]
Dialogue: 0.0:35:31.51.0:35:32.55.Default..0.0.0..Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:35.51.0:35:36.93.Default..0.0.0..[sizzling]
Dialogue: 0.0:35:37.01.0:35:37.85.Default..0.0.0..Okay…
Dialogue: 0.0:35:39.39.0:35:41.31.Default..0.0.0..[music fades]
Dialogue: 0.0:35:41.39.0:35:42.68.Default..0.0.0..[chuckles softly]
Dialogue: 0.0:35:43.98.0:35:45.60.Default..0.0.0..- What was that for?\N- Just…
Dialogue: 0.0:35:46.23.0:35:49.19.Default..0.0.0..…to thank you for this wonderful party.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:50.48.0:35:52.90.Default..0.0.0..All my favorite people are right…
Dialogue: 0.0:35:54.65.0:35:55.32.Default..0.0.0..…here.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:56.82.0:35:58.41.Default..0.0.0..Happy birthday. Ed.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:00.91.0:36:01.74.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine chuckles]
Dialogue: 0.0:36:04.45.0:36:05.79.Default..0.0.0..Uh-- She's here.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:11.96.0:36:13.17.Default..0.0.0..Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:14.38.0:36:17.34.Default..0.0.0..- [exhales]\N- Tony. you're acting so nervous!
Dialogue: 0.0:36:17.43.0:36:18.68.Default..0.0.0..What? I'm not nervous.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:20.18.0:36:23.72.Default..0.0.0..[sighs] I just really\Nwant them to approve.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:24.52.0:36:25.52.Default..0.0.0..Of what?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:26.23.0:36:29.02.Default..0.0.0..I don't know. Uh. you know. me. us.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:29.10.0:36:31.23.Default..0.0.0..[scoffs] You've got nothing\Nto worry about.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:32.11.0:36:33.57.Default..0.0.0..My mom loves you.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:36.19.0:36:37.20.Default..0.0.0..What about your dad?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:38.20.0:36:39.78.Default..0.0.0..["What It Is?"\Nby Curtis Liggins Indications playing]
Dialogue: 0.0:36:39.87.0:36:41.41.Default..0.0.0..- [chuckles]\N- Your dad doesn't like me?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:41.49.0:36:42.83.Default..0.0.0..- [laughing] Stop!\N- Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:42.91.0:36:45.29.Default..0.0.0..- You're telling me this now?\N- I didn't say that! Come on.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:46.87.0:36:48.87.Default..0.0.0..What's with the tie? It's not a funeral.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:48.96.0:36:50.42.Default..0.0.0..[Tony] So now I'm not even dressed right.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:50.50.0:36:51.84.Default..0.0.0..- [Judy laughs]\N- Oh. my God.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:51.92.0:36:53.50.Default..0.0.0..[chuckling]
Dialogue: 0.0:36:53.59.0:36:55.05.Default..0.0.0..All right. Where are we?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:55.13.0:36:56.26.Default..0.0.0..Is she here?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:56.34.0:36:58.01.Default..0.0.0..- Oh! Aw…\N- Happy birthday. Dad!
Dialogue: 0.0:36:58.34.0:36:59.93.Default..0.0.0..- Thank you. sweetie.\N- Hey. Mom.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:00.01.0:37:02.43.Default..0.0.0..- Tommy?\N- Dad. it's Tony!
Dialogue: 0.0:37:02.51.0:37:04.26.Default..0.0.0..- That's what I said.\N- Happy birthday. Mr. Warren.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:04.35.0:37:06.73.Default..0.0.0..- Thank you.\N- Tony. you look so handsome.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:06.81.0:37:08.19.Default..0.0.0..Oh. please. come on in.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:08.27.0:37:10.15.Default..0.0.0..Hey. what's with the tie?\NIt's not a funeral.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:10.23.0:37:11.61.Default..0.0.0..- [forced chuckle]\N- [chuckling]
Dialogue: 0.0:37:13.27.0:37:14.15.Default..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:14.23.0:37:16.23.Default..0.0.0..[chattering]
Dialogue: 0.0:37:18.24.0:37:19.53.Default..0.0.0..Judy?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:19.61.0:37:22.57.Default..0.0.0..- Father Gordon. Hi!\N- Oh. my goodness!
Dialogue: 0.0:37:22.66.0:37:24.70.Default..0.0.0..- [Father Gordon chuckles]\N- It's so good to see you.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:25.41.0:37:27.66.Default..0.0.0..- Honey?\N- [sighs] You have gotten taller.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:27.75.0:37:28.79.Default..0.0.0..[laughs]
Dialogue: 0.0:37:28.87.0:37:30.12.Default..0.0.0..He always says that.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:30.21.0:37:33.00.Default..0.0.0..Um. this is my boyfriend. Tony.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:33.75.0:37:36.55.Default..0.0.0..Tony. this is my Father Gordon.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:36.63.0:37:37.59.Default..0.0.0..[giggles]
Dialogue: 0.0:37:37.67.0:37:39.42.Default..0.0.0..He used to work with my mom and dad.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:39.51.0:37:41.55.Default..0.0.0..- It's nice to meet you. Tony.\N- And you.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:41.64.0:37:43.76.Default..0.0.0..So. what do you do?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:44.35.0:37:47.47.Default..0.0.0..Oh. uh… I am between jobs. actually.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:47.56.0:37:48.60.Default..0.0.0..Oh. okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:48.68.0:37:50.10.Default..0.0.0..Tony was a police officer.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:50.60.0:37:52.15.Default..0.0.0..Call it early retirement.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:52.52.0:37:54.73.Default..0.0.0..You're quite young for retirement. son.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:54.82.0:37:55.86.Default..0.0.0..[Father Gordon] Huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:57.32.0:37:58.61.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. it's. uh…
Dialogue: 0.0:37:58.69.0:37:59.90.Default..0.0.0..It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:01.66.0:38:03.87.Default..0.0.0..All right.\NBe careful not to touch anything.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:05.16.0:38:08.83.Default..0.0.0..So. everything you see in there\Nis either haunted. cursed.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:08.91.0:38:11.12.Default..0.0.0..or has been used in some sort of. uh…
Dialogue: 0.0:38:12.21.0:38:13.71.Default..0.0.0..ritualistic practice.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:16.17.0:38:17.05.Default..0.0.0..What's in there?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:18.38.0:38:19.51.Default..0.0.0..All the skeletons.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:20.88.0:38:22.13.Default..0.0.0..What? Wait. really?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:23.47.0:38:24.68.Default..0.0.0..Baby. hand me my beer.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:26.93.0:38:27.81.Default..0.0.0..Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:27.89.0:38:29.89.Default..0.0.0..[pop music playing over speakers]
Dialogue: 0.0:38:31.27.0:38:33.27.Default..0.0.0..[partygoers chattering]
Dialogue: 0.0:38:35.06.0:38:36.06.Default..0.0.0..Maybe one more?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:39.07.0:38:40.03.Default..0.0.0..Hey.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:40.94.0:38:41.90.Default..0.0.0..Smells good.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:45.37.0:38:46.99.Default..0.0.0..S-Sorry. uh. I'm Tony.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:48.29.0:38:49.24.Default..0.0.0..I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:50.12.0:38:51.50.Default..0.0.0..You're Judy's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:52.54.0:38:53.33.Default..0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:53.42.0:38:55.33.Default..0.0.0..Brad Hamilton.\NI used to work with the Warrens.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:56.00.0:38:57.13.Default..0.0.0..Oh…
Dialogue: 0.0:38:57.84.0:39:00.01.Default..0.0.0..[whispering] What. like.\Non their investigations?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:00.09.0:39:01.21.Default..0.0.0..Here and there. yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:01.30.0:39:05.55.Default..0.0.0..Sometimes consulting.\Nsometimes… security.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:07.93.0:39:10.56.Default..0.0.0..Hey. did you ever see an exorcism?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:10.89.0:39:12.31.Default..0.0.0..Did I ever see an exorcism?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:14.14.0:39:15.35.Default..0.0.0..[whispering] Did I ever see an exorcism?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:18.36.0:39:21.28.Default..0.0.0..Front row. baby. Right there.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:21.90.0:39:23.32.Default..0.0.0..That's a battle scar.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:23.40.0:39:25.53.Default..0.0.0..She nearly bit off my entire cheek.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:25.61.0:39:26.41.Default..0.0.0..She did that?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:26.49.0:39:29.37.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. [chuckling]\NAnd they say Rhode Island's boring.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:29.45.0:39:32.75.Default..0.0.0..[sharp inhale] I don't know.\NWhy don't you get a bun. Tony?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:33.79.0:39:35.79.Default..0.0.0..[partygoers chatting faintly downstairs]
Dialogue: 0.0:39:39.00.0:39:40.34.Default..0.0.0..[chuckles softly]
Dialogue: 0.0:40:08.82.0:40:10.87.Default..0.0.0..[creaking]
Dialogue: 0.0:40:16.58.0:40:18.58.Default..0.0.0..[Judy breathing heavily]
Dialogue: 0.0:40:27.63.0:40:28.76.Default..0.0.0..[sharp inhale]
Dialogue: 0.0:40:29.26.0:40:33.85.Default..0.0.0..- [breath shuddering]\N- [creaking continues]
Dialogue: 0.0:40:35.64.0:40:39.40.Default..0.0.0..[trembling whisper]\N♪ {\i1}Lucy Locket lost her pocket {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:40:40.69.0:40:42.57.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Kitty Fisher found it{\i0} ♪
Dialogue: 0.0:40:43.57.0:40:46.65.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Not a penny was there in it {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:40:48.49.0:40:50.24.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Only ribbon 'round it {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:40:52.78.0:40:53.87.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}You're… {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:40:56.25.0:40:57.33.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Not… {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:40:59.71.0:41:01.84.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- {\i0}♪ {\i1}…There {\i0}♪\N- [creaking halts]
Dialogue: 0.0:41:03.17.0:41:05.17.Default..0.0.0..[sighs]
Dialogue: 0.0:41:08.97.0:41:10.09.Default..0.0.0..[relieved sigh]
Dialogue: 0.0:41:10.59.0:41:11.97.Default..0.0.0..- [rapid knock]\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 0.0:41:13.18.0:41:14.89.Default..0.0.0..- Sorry.\N- [panting]
Dialogue: 0.0:41:15.60.0:41:16.39.Default..0.0.0..You okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:41:18.56.0:41:19.39.Default..0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:20.31.0:41:23.65.Default..0.0.0..Did you… see something?
Dialogue: 0.0:41:24.77.0:41:25.94.Default..0.0.0..It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:26.03.0:41:26.86.Default..0.0.0..Hey.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:27.49.0:41:31.11.Default..0.0.0..I'm sorry. This is weird.\NI'm-- I'm being weird.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:31.66.0:41:32.70.Default..0.0.0..I…
Dialogue: 0.0:41:34.91.0:41:36.24.Default..0.0.0..I love weird.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:37.33.0:41:38.41.Default..0.0.0..[laughs]
Dialogue: 0.0:41:38.50.0:41:41.63.Default..0.0.0..[stammering] I mean. I love you.\NI love… you.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:44.88.0:41:47.92.Default..0.0.0..Hey. what were you saying. when I came in?
Dialogue: 0.0:41:48.01.0:41:49.22.Default..0.0.0..[Judy] Um…
Dialogue: 0.0:41:50.05.0:41:51.93.Default..0.0.0..Just this trick my mom taught me.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:52.39.0:41:53.55.Default..0.0.0..What kinda trick?
Dialogue: 0.0:41:55.60.0:41:56.72.Default..0.0.0..Um…
Dialogue: 0.0:41:58.52.0:42:00.85.Default..0.0.0..It's how I learned to deal with my…
Dialogue: 0.0:42:01.77.0:42:03.36.Default..0.0.0..…um. senses.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:04.61.0:42:05.73.Default..0.0.0..How to shut them out.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:07.57.0:42:09.86.Default..0.0.0..Okay. Um. how did it go again?
Dialogue: 0.0:42:10.65.0:42:12.74.Default..0.0.0..- [scoffs]\N- No. seriously. Teach me.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:12.82.0:42:13.99.Default..0.0.0..It's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:15.16.0:42:16.24.Default..0.0.0..I wanna know.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:16.87.0:42:19.08.Default..0.0.0..You can't be embarrassed in front of me.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:19.83.0:42:20.66.Default..0.0.0..Please?
Dialogue: 0.0:42:21.29.0:42:22.96.Default..0.0.0..Okay. but you can't laugh.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:23.04.0:42:25.29.Default..0.0.0..- I will not laugh.\N- [nervous chuckle]
Dialogue: 0.0:42:26.29.0:42:27.38.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Lucy Locket… {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:42:28.05.0:42:30.30.Default..0.0.0..- [suppressed snicker]\N- ♪ {\i1}Lucy Locket… {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:42:31.09.0:42:32.51.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}…Lost her pocket {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:42:33.22.0:42:34.51.Default..0.0.0..- Poor Lucy.\N- [laughs]
Dialogue: 0.0:42:35.35.0:42:39.10.Default..0.0.0..No… Actually. wait. [clears throat]\NI came in. You had your eyes closed.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:39.93.0:42:41.98.Default..0.0.0..That's gotta be part of it. no?
Dialogue: 0.0:42:42.98.0:42:43.98.Default..0.0.0..[whispering] Fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:42:48.36.0:42:50.65.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Lucy Locket… {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:42:50.74.0:42:52.36.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Lucy Locket… {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:42:52.45.0:42:54.07.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}…Lost her pocket {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:42:54.16.0:42:55.95.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}…Lost her pocket {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:42:56.03.0:42:58.03.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Kitty Fisher found it {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:42:58.12.0:42:59.24.Default..0.0.0..- ♪ {\i1}Kitty Fisher… {\i0}♪\N- ♪ {\i1}Not a… {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.0:43:00.16.0:43:01.33.Default..0.0.0..[whispering] Hey.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:01.41.0:43:02.12.Default..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:43:02.87.0:43:03.75.Default..0.0.0..Cheating.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:04.42.0:43:05.38.Default..0.0.0..Sorry.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:14.43.0:43:15.51.Default..0.0.0..Oh! I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:15.59.0:43:16.76.Default..0.0.0..- Mom!\N- Mrs. Warren!
Dialogue: 0.0:43:16.85.0:43:18.01.Default..0.0.0..[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0.0:43:18.10.0:43:19.10.Default..0.0.0..Um…
Dialogue: 0.0:43:19.68.0:43:21.06.Default..0.0.0..Tony. Ed was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:21.14.0:43:22.93.Default..0.0.0..He's taking some of the guys\Nto the garage.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:25.85.0:43:27.31.Default..0.0.0..Oh. so… Like. me?
Dialogue: 0.0:43:28.15.0:43:29.57.Default..0.0.0..Yes. if-- if you want.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:29.98.0:43:32.15.Default..0.0.0..Uh. yeah. Sure.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:37.91.0:43:39.95.Default..0.0.0..I should probably…
Dialogue: 0.0:43:41.04.0:43:42.12.Default..0.0.0..Judy. wait.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:51.59.0:43:52.67.Default..0.0.0..What's going on?
Dialogue: 0.0:43:55.01.0:43:56.51.Default..0.0.0..Nothing. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:43:57.80.0:43:59.47.Default..0.0.0..The other night. at the restaurant?
Dialogue: 0.0:43:59.55.0:44:00.81.Default..0.0.0..It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:03.48.0:44:06.23.Default..0.0.0..You're seeing things\Nmore often now. aren't you?
Dialogue: 0.0:44:08.81.0:44:09.48.Default..0.0.0..No.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:12.19.0:44:14.07.Default..0.0.0..Do you remember what we practiced?
Dialogue: 0.0:44:14.78.0:44:15.95.Default..0.0.0..I can handle it.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:16.03.0:44:19.57.Default..0.0.0..You can't. Judy. you can't.\NYou need to shut it out.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:20.49.0:44:24.41.Default..0.0.0..Trust me. after a lifetime of this.\NI promise you.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:24.83.0:44:26.46.Default..0.0.0..you don't want it.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:27.92.0:44:28.96.Default..0.0.0..I got it.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:31.46.0:44:32.50.Default..0.0.0..I love you.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:36.22.0:44:37.47.Default..0.0.0..I love you too. Mom.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:46.02.0:44:48.14.Default..0.0.0..Should we go rescue Tony from your father?
Dialogue: 0.0:44:48.23.0:44:50.11.Default..0.0.0..- Please.\N- [both chuckling]
Dialogue: 0.0:44:51.11.0:44:52.44.Default..0.0.0..Thanks for the encouragement.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:53.40.0:44:55.03.Default..0.0.0..[Ed] There's a nice bounce!
Dialogue: 0.0:44:55.11.0:44:56.32.Default..0.0.0..Come on. Drew. you got this.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:56.40.0:44:58.20.Default..0.0.0..Get him. Get him.
Dialogue: 0.0:44:58.28.0:44:59.70.Default..0.0.0..[men] Oh!
Dialogue: 0.0:44:59.78.0:45:00.99.Default..0.0.0..[Ed laughing]
Dialogue: 0.0:45:01.07.0:45:02.95.Default..0.0.0..Tony! You're up.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:03.49.0:45:04.99.Default..0.0.0..["Let's Dance" by David Bowie playing]
Dialogue: 0.0:45:05.08.0:45:05.87.Default..0.0.0..Sure.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:06.33.0:45:07.21.Default..0.0.0..- All good?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:07.29.0:45:08.25.Default..0.0.0..Good luck. buddy.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:13.42.0:45:15.42.Default..0.0.0..[Tony grunting]
Dialogue: 0.0:45:17.05.0:45:19.13.Default..0.0.0..[scattered cheering]
Dialogue: 0.0:45:19.22.0:45:20.55.Default..0.0.0..- [Tony] All right.\N- Jacket off!
Dialogue: 0.0:45:20.64.0:45:22.14.Default..0.0.0..- The jacket. I got it.\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0.0:45:22.22.0:45:23.81.Default..0.0.0..- [sighs] Ready?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:23.89.0:45:24.85.Default..0.0.0..You need to hop around a little more?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:24.93.0:45:26.56.Default..0.0.0..- No. I'm good. sir. I'm good.\N- All right. Here we go. Ready?
Dialogue: 0.0:45:28.31.0:45:29.48.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}♪ Let's play ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:45:29.56.0:45:31.10.Default..0.0.0..- [Lorraine and Judy laughing]\N- Whoa!
Dialogue: 0.0:45:31.77.0:45:33.57.Default..0.0.0..[scattered cheers]
Dialogue: 0.0:45:33.65.0:45:35.28.Default..0.0.0..- [Tony] One more.\N- [Ed] All right.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:36.86.0:45:37.99.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}♪ Let's sway ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:45:39.57.0:45:43.58.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}♪ Under the moonlight{\i0}\N{\i1}The serious moonlight ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:45:45.49.0:45:47.12.Default..0.0.0..[spectators] Oh!
Dialogue: 0.0:45:47.83.0:45:50.04.Default..0.0.0..[cheering. laughing]
Dialogue: 0.0:45:50.12.0:45:51.92.Default..0.0.0..[laughing heartily]
Dialogue: 0.0:45:52.00.0:45:54.04.Default..0.0.0..Twenty-one. eighteen!
Dialogue: 0.0:45:54.13.0:45:55.50.Default..0.0.0..- [chuckling]\N- [Tony] Good game.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:55.59.0:45:58.09.Default..0.0.0..[Drew] Tough luck. Tony.\NAlmost thought you had a chance.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:58.17.0:45:59.34.Default..0.0.0..- Congratulations.\N- Oh. man.
Dialogue: 0.0:45:59.42.0:46:00.76.Default..0.0.0..- [Judy] That was so good.\N- Nice job.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:00.84.0:46:02.30.Default..0.0.0..- We got a winner.\N- Why did I hit it?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:02.39.0:46:04.30.Default..0.0.0..- Sorry.\N- [exhales]
Dialogue: 0.0:46:05.18.0:46:07.02.Default..0.0.0..- [deep breath]\N- You okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:07.10.0:46:08.52.Default..0.0.0..- [panting] Yeah.\N- [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0.0:46:08.60.0:46:09.68.Default..0.0.0..Still undefeated.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:09.77.0:46:11.52.Default..0.0.0..I'm gonna get another drink.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:11.60.0:46:13.86.Default..0.0.0..Oh. I'll come. Uh.\NMom. Dad. you want something?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:13.94.0:46:15.61.Default..0.0.0..- No. thank you. sweetheart.\N- You good?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:15.69.0:46:17.03.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. I'm good. I'm good.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:18.32.0:46:19.28.Default..0.0.0..[Judy] We have beers?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:20.32.0:46:21.99.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah.\N- [Ed] Whoo.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:22.49.0:46:23.53.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine] Don't think I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:23.62.0:46:24.82.Default..0.0.0..- It's spick and span.\N- I'm trying.
Dialogue: 0.0:46:24.95.0:46:26.74.Default..0.0.0..- [Lorraine] Yeah. [chuckles]\N- [Tony] This is. uh…
Dialogue: 0.0:46:26.83.0:46:28.29.Default..0.0.0..Sorry to interrupt. Um…
Dialogue: 0.0:46:28.79.0:46:32.00.Default..0.0.0..Actually. I. um… You know.\NI was hoping to say something?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:32.08.0:46:33.50.Default..0.0.0..Sure. What's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0.0:46:34.21.0:46:36.09.Default..0.0.0..[stammers] Yeah. well. um…
Dialogue: 0.0:46:38.71.0:46:42.88.Default..0.0.0..You know. it's good that Judy's gone.\N'cause what I wanted to say was. um…
Dialogue: 0.0:46:48.10.0:46:49.22.Default..0.0.0..I'm just gonna…
Dialogue: 0.0:46:50.81.0:46:51.60.Default..0.0.0..[Tony] Uh…
Dialogue: 0.0:46:52.44.0:46:53.85.Default..0.0.0..- [gasps]\N- So…
Dialogue: 0.0:46:58.90.0:47:01.36.Default..0.0.0..I bought this a week after I met her.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:03.49.0:47:07.45.Default..0.0.0..Soon. I know. and I know\Nwe've only been dating for six months.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:07.87.0:47:08.79.Default..0.0.0..but…
Dialogue: 0.0:47:10.41.0:47:11.91.Default..0.0.0..You know. when you know. you know.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:12.00.0:47:15.21.Default..0.0.0..And I-I just--\NI can't imagine my life without her.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:16.88.0:47:17.96.Default..0.0.0..So…
Dialogue: 0.0:47:19.13.0:47:24.01.Default..0.0.0..what I'm trying to say is.\NI-I… I would love to have your blessing.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:28.81.0:47:30.60.Default..0.0.0..It's beautiful. Tony.
Dialogue: 0.0:47:31.72.0:47:32.98.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine chuckles]
Dialogue: 0.0:47:51.87.0:47:53.33.Default..0.0.0..You do know…
Dialogue: 0.0:47:54.33.0:47:57.92.Default..0.0.0..…that our family\Nis not like other families?
Dialogue: 0.0:48:04.13.0:48:05.93.Default..0.0.0..And Judy. um…
Dialogue: 0.0:48:09.97.0:48:12.31.Default..0.0.0..…she's our little girl. [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0.0:48:13.35.0:48:17.85.Default..0.0.0..And. um. you know. you're right.\Nit has been a very short time.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:19.36.0:48:22.53.Default..0.0.0..But we barely knew each other\Nwhen we got engaged.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:22.61.0:48:24.32.Default..0.0.0..- Well--\N- Ed was shipping out.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:25.15.0:48:26.95.Default..0.0.0..But I think that… I don't know.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:27.49.0:48:29.37.Default..0.0.0..I think that we just knew.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:32.74.0:48:33.79.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine] Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:35.12.0:48:37.62.Default..0.0.0..Of course. you have our blessing.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:37.71.0:48:39.38.Default..0.0.0..[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0.0:48:39.46.0:48:41.17.Default..0.0.0..[inhales] Mr. Warren?
Dialogue: 0.0:48:41.25.0:48:42.59.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. um…
Dialogue: 0.0:48:44.63.0:48:47.63.Default..0.0.0..Tony. um… You're a good kid…
Dialogue: 0.0:48:47.72.0:48:48.59.Default..0.0.0..Ed…
Dialogue: 0.0:48:48.68.0:48:51.39.Default..0.0.0..And… Well. they've only known\Neach other six months.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:51.47.0:48:52.60.Default..0.0.0..Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:52.68.0:48:54.31.Default..0.0.0..But she just said that you guys--
Dialogue: 0.0:48:54.39.0:48:55.27.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah. well. that…\N- Yeah…
Dialogue: 0.0:48:55.35.0:48:57.14.Default..0.0.0..…was a-a different time.
Dialogue: 0.0:48:59.02.0:49:00.15.Default..0.0.0..Okay. um…
Dialogue: 0.0:49:01.73.0:49:03.36.Default..0.0.0..Maybe this was too early?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:03.73.0:49:04.94.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah. there we go.\N- No.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:05.03.0:49:07.99.Default..0.0.0..So. I will come back in a month and--
Dialogue: 0.0:49:08.07.0:49:09.07.Default..0.0.0..A month?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:09.78.0:49:10.78.Default..0.0.0..Ed…
Dialogue: 0.0:49:14.29.0:49:15.29.Default..0.0.0..What is that?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:16.91.0:49:18.25.Default..0.0.0..- Sh…\N- Oh.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:18.33.0:49:19.21.Default..0.0.0..- [ring clatters]\N- [Judy gasps]
Dialogue: 0.0:49:27.63.0:49:28.88.Default..0.0.0..Is that for me?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:40.02.0:49:40.77.Default..0.0.0..Yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:42.02.0:49:44.40.Default..0.0.0..- Judy. I was asking--\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0.0:49:45.07.0:49:48.36.Default..0.0.0..Yes! Obviously. yes! [laugh]
Dialogue: 0.0:49:50.03.0:49:51.03.Default..0.0.0..Yes!
Dialogue: 0.0:49:54.28.0:49:56.62.Default..0.0.0..- [chuckles]\N- It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0.0:49:57.75.0:49:59.66.Default..0.0.0..Is this why\Nyou were so nervous in the car?
Dialogue: 0.0:49:59.75.0:50:01.37.Default..0.0.0..- Sure was.\N- [Lorraine and Judy laugh]
Dialogue: 0.0:50:01.92.0:50:04.84.Default..0.0.0..- Did you see it?\N- I did! I did.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:04.92.0:50:05.88.Default..0.0.0..It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:05.96.0:50:07.88.Default..0.0.0..- Oh. honey.\N- Thank you. sir.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:07.96.0:50:09.88.Default..0.0.0..- Thank you.\N- Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:09.97.0:50:11.09.Default..0.0.0..So pretty.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:12.47.0:50:13.93.Default..0.0.0..- You happy?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:14.47.0:50:15.97.Default..0.0.0..- Congrats. Tony.\N- Thanks. man.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:16.64.0:50:18.64.Default..0.0.0..You know. Tony. he seems like a good egg.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:18.73.0:50:20.56.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. yeah…
Dialogue: 0.0:50:21.89.0:50:24.11.Default..0.0.0..Judy's got good instincts.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:24.19.0:50:27.94.Default..0.0.0..You just. have to let her go.\Nlet her walk her own path.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:28.36.0:50:29.19.Default..0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:29.65.0:50:31.70.Default..0.0.0..Oh. uh. by the way…
Dialogue: 0.0:50:32.74.0:50:34.41.Default..0.0.0..we've had a couple calls.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:34.49.0:50:37.45.Default..0.0.0..Some families reaching out.\NThey could use your…
Dialogue: 0.0:50:38.83.0:50:40.29.Default..0.0.0..special assistance.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:40.37.0:50:41.75.Default..0.0.0..So. what are we talking about?\NAre they local. or--
Dialogue: 0.0:50:41.83.0:50:42.83.Default..0.0.0..Ed.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:43.83.0:50:45.08.Default..0.0.0..- [groans]\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:45.67.0:50:48.34.Default..0.0.0..We're sorry. Father.\NThose days are behind us now.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:48.42.0:50:50.55.Default..0.0.0..I know. I guess I just--
Dialogue: 0.0:50:51.88.0:50:53.05.Default..0.0.0..I just had to try.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:53.72.0:50:55.30.Default..0.0.0..- For old times' sake.\N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:56.89.0:50:58.31.Default..0.0.0..- Happy birthday.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.0:50:58.39.0:50:59.93.Default..0.0.0..You look good for an old guy.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:00.89.0:51:02.77.Default..0.0.0..[Ed and Lorraine chuckling]
Dialogue: 0.0:51:03.98.0:51:05.19.Default..0.0.0..[sighs]
Dialogue: 0.0:51:27.13.0:51:28.92.Default..0.0.0..[Dawn] {\i1}We're just gonna pretend.{\i0}\N{\i1}like nothing's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:51:29.00.0:51:31.84.Default..0.0.0..Father Jensen has submitted\Nour case to the archdiocese.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:31.92.0:51:33.17.Default..0.0.0..And so what?
Dialogue: 0.0:51:33.47.0:51:35.89.Default..0.0.0..You're just gonna let us\Nlive in a haunted house?
Dialogue: 0.0:51:35.97.0:51:37.18.Default..0.0.0..Don't talk to your father like that!
Dialogue: 0.0:51:37.26.0:51:38.72.Default..0.0.0..It's all right. I got this. Mom.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:38.81.0:51:41.35.Default..0.0.0..Just. please. stop fighting!
Dialogue: 0.0:51:41.43.0:51:42.77.Default..0.0.0..Oh. honey…
Dialogue: 0.0:51:43.27.0:51:44.14.Default..0.0.0..It's okay. honey.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:44.23.0:51:46.27.Default..0.0.0..Please. Dad. can't we got to a motel?
Dialogue: 0.0:51:46.35.0:51:49.32.Default..0.0.0..There's eight of us. sweetie.\NWe can't afford that.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:49.40.0:51:51.28.Default..0.0.0..As I was saying. Father Jensen has said--
Dialogue: 0.0:51:51.36.0:51:52.44.Default..0.0.0.."Father Jensen says."
Dialogue: 0.0:51:52.53.0:51:54.11.Default..0.0.0..- God. I've heard that before.\N- The church has a process.
Dialogue: 0.0:51:55.15.0:51:58.16.Default..0.0.0..They work with people\Nwho come and document…
Dialogue: 0.0:51:59.12.0:52:00.03.Default..0.0.0..these things.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:00.12.0:52:01.08.Default..0.0.0.."These things?"
Dialogue: 0.0:52:01.16.0:52:02.79.Default..0.0.0..To prove it's all real!
Dialogue: 0.0:52:03.16.0:52:05.08.Default..0.0.0.."To prove it's all real?"
Dialogue: 0.0:52:05.54.0:52:07.21.Default..0.0.0..It's real!
Dialogue: 0.0:52:07.29.0:52:09.13.Default..0.0.0..- It wants to kill us!\N- No. no.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:09.21.0:52:10.25.Default..0.0.0..No. it does!
Dialogue: 0.0:52:12.55.0:52:14.67.Default..0.0.0..[crying]
Dialogue: 0.0:52:14.76.0:52:17.26.Default..0.0.0..You-- You don't believe us. do you?
Dialogue: 0.0:52:17.34.0:52:18.39.Default..0.0.0..- No. no. Dawn.\N- Do you?
Dialogue: 0.0:52:18.47.0:52:19.80.Default..0.0.0..- that is not what I am saying.\N- No. you don't believe us.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:19.89.0:52:21.51.Default..0.0.0..- That is not what I'm saying!\N- You don't believe us.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:21.60.0:52:23.06.Default..0.0.0..just 'cause it hasn't happened to you.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:23.14.0:52:24.52.Default..0.0.0..It's happening to all of us!
Dialogue: 0.0:52:24.60.0:52:27.23.Default..0.0.0..Not the same way it's happened to me. Dad!
Dialogue: 0.0:52:27.56.0:52:30.65.Default..0.0.0..I cannot live like this anymore.\NNone of us can!
Dialogue: 0.0:52:32.32.0:52:33.40.Default..0.0.0..Either you don't believe us.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:33.48.0:52:35.99.Default..0.0.0..or you can't do anything about it.\NWhich is it?
Dialogue: 0.0:52:41.41.0:52:42.74.Default..0.0.0..- Jesus fucking Christ…\N- Dawn…
Dialogue: 0.0:52:42.83.0:52:43.79.Default..0.0.0..- Hey!\N- No. no.
Dialogue: 0.0:52:43.87.0:52:44.70.Default..0.0.0..- I'm not gonna wait. Don't.\N- Just leave it. No. no. Hon…
Dialogue: 0.0:52:44.79.0:52:47.08.Default..0.0.0..Oh. no. Dawn. Come…
