Dialogue: 0.0:58:20.46.0:58:22.75.Default..0.0.0..No one's here. honey. No one's here!
Dialogue: 0.0:58:23.71.0:58:26.34.Default..0.0.0..- [Heather] He's in here! [sobs]\N- [grandma] Heather! Poor. baby.
