Dialogue: 0.0:59:54.34.0:59:55.97.Default..0.0.0..Oh. Brenda… How's your family?
Dialogue: 0.0:59:56.05.0:59:57.76.Default..0.0.0..Oh. good. good. good.
Dialogue: 0.0:59:57.85.1:00:01.72.Default..0.0.0..You know. maybe when we're done.\Nyou can tell me my future?
Dialogue: 0.1:00:01.81.1:00:05.52.Default..0.0.0..I'm kidding. I know that's not your thing!\NYou've got your investigations and all.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:05.60.1:00:07.56.Default..0.0.0..- Well. not anymore.\N- [Brenda] Okay. So. Mrs. Warren.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:07.65.1:00:09.15.Default..0.0.0..Maureen'll get you a coffee or something.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:09.23.1:00:12.19.Default..0.0.0..And sweetie. I'll take you back.\NWe'll try on that beautiful dress!
Dialogue: 0.1:00:13.11.1:00:14.15.Default..0.0.0..[Brenda gasps]
Dialogue: 0.1:00:18.41.1:00:19.74.Default..0.0.0..[sighs]
Dialogue: 0.1:00:19.83.1:00:21.95.Default..0.0.0..Wish I could meet a guy like Tony.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:22.04.1:00:23.58.Default..0.0.0..- What about Dom?\N- Ugh.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:23.66.1:00:26.04.Default..0.0.0..We broke up. Again.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:26.58.1:00:29.46.Default..0.0.0..I'm sorry. There's plenty\Nmore fish in the sea.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:29.54.1:00:30.75.Default..0.0.0..[Brenda] You're very sweet.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:30.84.1:00:32.09.Default..0.0.0..You were too pretty for him. anyway.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:32.17.1:00:33.55.Default..0.0.0..- [scoffs] Stop!\N- [phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0.1:00:33.63.1:00:35.63.Default..0.0.0..- Ow!\N- Oh. I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0.1:00:35.72.1:00:37.09.Default..0.0.0..Looks like I nicked you there.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:37.18.1:00:39.97.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah.\N- [phone ringing]
Dialogue: 0.1:00:40.05.1:00:41.39.Default..0.0.0..[shouts] Maureen?
Dialogue: 0.1:00:43.52.1:00:45.64.Default..0.0.0..- [ringing continues]\N- You gonna get that?
Dialogue: 0.1:00:47.81.1:00:50.02.Default..0.0.0..That girl's an idiot. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0.1:00:50.11.1:00:52.57.Default..0.0.0..[ringing continues]
Dialogue: 0.1:00:56.11.1:00:58.11.Default..0.0.0..[ringing stops]
Dialogue: 0.1:01:19.93.1:01:21.05.Default..0.0.0..[light gasp]
Dialogue: 0.1:01:38.57.1:01:42.70.Default..0.0.0..[light panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:01:53.13.1:01:55.13.Default..0.0.0..[door opens]
Dialogue: 0.1:01:55.96.1:01:57.97.Default..0.0.0..[sighs]
Dialogue: 0.1:01:59.17.1:02:01.68.Default..0.0.0..I was starting to get\Nreally claustrophobic.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:03.76.1:02:05.18.Default..0.0.0..[door closes]
Dialogue: 0.1:02:08.89.1:02:09.89.Default..0.0.0..Brenda?
Dialogue: 0.1:02:18.03.1:02:20.07.Default..0.0.0..You okay down there. Brenda?
Dialogue: 0.1:02:20.15.1:02:23.07.Default..0.0.0..- [rustling]\N- Ow.
Dialogue: 0.1:02:23.16.1:02:25.37.Default..0.0.0..[ethereal chuckling]
Dialogue: 0.1:02:30.71.1:02:31.92.Default..0.0.0..[whispers] Brenda?
Dialogue: 0.1:02:43.09.1:02:45.39.Default..0.0.0..[ragged breathing]
Dialogue: 0.1:02:46.35.1:02:48.52.Default..0.0.0..[Judy screams]
Dialogue: 0.1:02:48.60.1:02:52.27.Default..0.0.0..- [groaning]\N- [crying]
Dialogue: 0.1:02:52.35.1:02:56.15.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Lucy Locket lost her pocket{\i0}\N{\i1}Kitty Fisher found it {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.1:02:56.23.1:02:59.69.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Not a penny was there in it{\i0}\N{\i1}Only ribbon 'round it {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.1:02:59.78.1:03:01.57.Default..0.0.0..- [shrieks] Mom!\N- [demon grunting]
Dialogue: 0.1:03:01.65.1:03:05.24.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Lucy Locket lost her pocket{\i0}\N{\i1}Kitty Fisher found it {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.1:03:05.32.1:03:07.70.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Not a penny there was in it{\i0}\N{\i1}Only ribbon 'round it {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.1:03:07.78.1:03:12.00.Default..0.0.0..- [Judy wailing]\N- [inhales. cackles]
Dialogue: 0.1:03:12.08.1:03:13.79.Default..0.0.0..[Judy] ♪ {\i1}You're not there! {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.1:03:13.87.1:03:17.59.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:03:22.47.1:03:24.26.Default..0.0.0..[breathing heavily]
Dialogue: 0.1:03:28.51.1:03:29.93.Default..0.0.0..[sighs]
Dialogue: 0.1:03:30.43.1:03:32.43.Default..0.0.0..- [gasps]\N- [glass clinks]
Dialogue: 0.1:03:34.85.1:03:38.15.Default..0.0.0..- [smashes]\N- [grunts]
Dialogue: 0.1:03:38.23.1:03:40.23.Default..0.0.0..[gasping. choking]
Dialogue: 0.1:03:40.98.1:03:43.07.Default..0.0.0..[sobs]
Dialogue: 0.1:03:43.15.1:03:45.03.Default..0.0.0..- [Lorraine] Judy!\N- [panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:03:45.11.1:03:48.45.Default..0.0.0..- What's wrong? Hey.\N- [panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:03:48.53.1:03:49.95.Default..0.0.0..What happened?
Dialogue: 0.1:03:50.04.1:03:54.29.Default..0.0.0..[crying echoes]
Dialogue: 0.1:03:55.25.1:03:56.46.Default..0.0.0..It's okay.
Dialogue: 0.1:03:56.54.1:03:59.96.Default..0.0.0..- [overlapping chatter]\N- [man] Mr. Smurl. Mr. Smurl.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:00.05.1:04:00.96.Default..0.0.0..- [EMT] Careful.\N- Jack.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:01.05.1:04:02.01.Default..0.0.0..Can you back off. please?
Dialogue: 0.1:04:02.09.1:04:02.88.Default..0.0.0..What's going on in your house?
Dialogue: 0.1:04:02.97.1:04:04.47.Default..0.0.0..- Please. can you make some room?\N- Back off!
Dialogue: 0.1:04:04.55.1:04:05.63.Default..0.0.0..Please. have some respect!
Dialogue: 0.1:04:05.72.1:04:07.14.Default..0.0.0..- Out of respect for my mother.\N- Please. back off!
Dialogue: 0.1:04:07.55.1:04:09.93.Default..0.0.0..- [Jack] Give us space. please!\N- [girl] Is she okay?
Dialogue: 0.1:04:10.01.1:04:11.18.Default..0.0.0..[Jack] For heaven's sake.\Noutta my face!
Dialogue: 0.1:04:11.27.1:04:12.22.Default..0.0.0..[man] Careful.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:12.31.1:04:13.85.Default..0.0.0..- [John] Go away!\N- [Jack] You'll be okay. Mom.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:13.93.1:04:15.94.Default..0.0.0..Kids. Grandma's gonna be fine.\Ndon't worry.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:16.35.1:04:17.56.Default..0.0.0..Dawn. look after your mother.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:17.65.1:04:18.65.Default..0.0.0..- Can you get out of my--\N- [chattering]
Dialogue: 0.1:04:18.73.1:04:20.44.Default..0.0.0..- Jack. I'll see you there. okay?\N- See you at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:20.52.1:04:21.78.Default..0.0.0..I'm gonna go with Ma.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:21.86.1:04:23.53.Default..0.0.0..- We'll be in touch. sweetie.\N- [John] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:24.61.1:04:25.61.Default..0.0.0..[Janet. quietly] Why won't it stop?
Dialogue: 0.1:04:25.70.1:04:26.66.Default..0.0.0..Mom. look.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:26.99.1:04:30.53.Default..0.0.0..- [car doors close]\N- [siren wails]
Dialogue: 0.1:04:32.12.1:04:35.00.Default..0.0.0..[chattering]
Dialogue: 0.1:04:36.00.1:04:38.17.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:04:39.33.1:04:41.17.Default..0.0.0..[dog groans]
Dialogue: 0.1:04:41.25.1:04:42.30.Default..0.0.0..[priest] Yes.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:43.46.1:04:46.09.Default..0.0.0..- That's Simon.\N- Oh. hey. Simon.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:46.84.1:04:48.43.Default..0.0.0..I grew up with a dog like this.
Dialogue: 0.1:04:48.51.1:04:50.72.Default..0.0.0..- Oh. you did?\N- Yeah. [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0.1:04:51.76.1:04:54.35.Default..0.0.0..Th-- That ambulance out there…
Dialogue: 0.1:04:55.52.1:04:56.56.Default..0.0.0..…who was that?
Dialogue: 0.1:05:00.56.1:05:01.86.Default..0.0.0..It's my mother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:03.23.1:05:05.11.Default..0.0.0..[inhales] Some…
Dialogue: 0.1:05:07.15.1:05:09.62.Default..0.0.0..Something pushed her down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:09.99.1:05:12.28.Default..0.0.0..- It's getting worse.\N- [sighs]
Dialogue: 0.1:05:12.37.1:05:13.87.Default..0.0.0..And we can't afford to leave.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:17.58.1:05:20.38.Default..0.0.0..- I'm so glad that you're here.\N- [sighs]
Dialogue: 0.1:05:20.75.1:05:22.84.Default..0.0.0..[sighs] We really thought that
Dialogue: 0.1:05:22.92.1:05:24.76.Default..0.0.0..the church had forgotten about us.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:25.67.1:05:27.80.Default..0.0.0..[priest] Mrs. Smurl. uh…
Dialogue: 0.1:05:29.97.1:05:32.01.Default..0.0.0..The church doesn't know I'm here.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:32.10.1:05:34.01.Default..0.0.0..I'm actually from Connecticut.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:34.10.1:05:37.14.Default..0.0.0..But I have worked\Nwith cases similar to yours.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:37.23.1:05:41.86.Default..0.0.0..and I have been following your story\Nvery closely on the news.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:42.90.1:05:44.78.Default..0.0.0..I thought I might be able to help.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:48.15.1:05:51.49.Default..0.0.0..In the name of the Father.\Nthe Son. and the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:51.57.1:05:52.99.Default..0.0.0..[water spattering]
Dialogue: 0.1:05:53.08.1:05:57.20.Default..0.0.0..In the name of the Father.\Nthe Son. and the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0.1:05:59.71.1:06:02.75.Default..0.0.0..In the name of the Father.\Nthe Son. and the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:02.83.1:06:06.30.Default..0.0.0..[door creaks]
Dialogue: 0.1:06:30.15.1:06:32.16.Default..0.0.0..[ragged breath]
Dialogue: 0.1:06:34.28.1:06:37.58.Default..0.0.0..In the name of the Father.\Nthe Son. and the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:43.29.1:06:46.29.Default..0.0.0..- [footsteps]\N- [holy water splashes]
Dialogue: 0.1:06:46.38.1:06:50.01.Default..0.0.0..In the name of the Father.\Nthe Son. and the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0.1:06:51.51.1:06:55.05.Default..0.0.0..[hissing]
Dialogue: 0.1:06:57.18.1:07:01.52.Default..0.0.0..In the name of the Father.\Nthe Son. and the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:01.60.1:07:05.52.Default..0.0.0..[hissing]
Dialogue: 0.1:07:07.77.1:07:13.28.Default..0.0.0..[whooshing]
Dialogue: 0.1:07:13.36.1:07:15.41.Default..0.0.0..[rumbling]
Dialogue: 0.1:07:17.33.1:07:18.29.Default..0.0.0..What happened down there?
Dialogue: 0.1:07:18.37.1:07:19.41.Default..0.0.0..Something's here.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:19.83.1:07:21.20.Default..0.0.0..- [briefcase clicks]\N- You're leaving?
Dialogue: 0.1:07:21.62.1:07:25.46.Default..0.0.0..We are gonna help you. [panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:07:25.88.1:07:27.29.Default..0.0.0..The church will listen to me.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:28.04.1:07:30.96.Default..0.0.0..I promise you. they'll listen.
Dialogue: 0.1:07:33.76.1:07:35.05.Default..0.0.0..[brakes squeak]
Dialogue: 0.1:07:35.14.1:07:37.14.Default..0.0.0..[horns honk in distance]
Dialogue: 0.1:07:44.35.1:07:46.56.Default..0.0.0..[door creaks]
Dialogue: 0.1:07:52.44.1:07:54.45.Default..0.0.0..[footsteps echo]
Dialogue: 0.1:07:59.95.1:08:04.12.Default..0.0.0..[whirring]
Dialogue: 0.1:08:07.17.1:08:09.29.Default..0.0.0..[typewriter tapping]
Dialogue: 0.1:08:11.13.1:08:12.84.Default..0.0.0..[whirring continues]
Dialogue: 0.1:08:13.67.1:08:14.67.Default..0.0.0..Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0.1:08:14.76.1:08:16.13.Default..0.0.0..Bishop McKenna. please.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:16.72.1:08:18.51.Default..0.0.0..Of course. And you are?
Dialogue: 0.1:08:18.60.1:08:19.85.Default..0.0.0..Father Gordon.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:19.93.1:08:20.93.Default..0.0.0..One minute.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:22.31.1:08:24.64.Default..0.0.0..[phone rings in office]
Dialogue: 0.1:08:24.73.1:08:26.81.Default..0.0.0..I have a Father Gordon.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:28.19.1:08:30.40.Default..0.0.0..- This is regarding?\N- The Smurls.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:30.48.1:08:32.69.Default..0.0.0..They're a family from West Pittston.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:32.78.1:08:33.99.Default..0.0.0..It's urgent.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:35.28.1:08:38.49.Default..0.0.0..He's here about a family\Nfrom West Pittston.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:38.57.1:08:39.70.Default..0.0.0..He says it's urgent.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:41.74.1:08:43.08.Default..0.0.0..All right.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:45.04.1:08:46.79.Default..0.0.0..He'll just be one moment.
Dialogue: 0.1:08:58.84.1:09:00.26.Default..0.0.0..[return dings]
Dialogue: 0.1:09:02.76.1:09:06.18.Default..0.0.0..[typing continues]
Dialogue: 0.1:09:09.06.1:09:11.61.Default..0.0.0..[secretary] Father? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0.1:09:11.73.1:09:13.65.Default..0.0.0..Yes. I'm… [chuckles]
Dialogue: 0.1:09:13.73.1:09:14.90.Default..0.0.0..I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0.1:09:26.62.1:09:28.58.Default..0.0.0..- [thwap]\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 0.1:09:28.67.1:09:31.92.Default..0.0.0..- [quiet]\N- [clock ticks]
Dialogue: 0.1:09:40.47.1:09:42.10.Default..0.0.0..Hel-- Hello?
Dialogue: 0.1:09:48.98.1:09:51.40.Default..0.0.0..[phone rings]
Dialogue: 0.1:09:59.95.1:10:02.41.Default..0.0.0..[phone rings]
Dialogue: 0.1:10:09.37.1:10:10.67.Default..0.0.0..[Judy's voice] {\i1}Father Gordon?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:10:11.12.1:10:13.46.Default..0.0.0..- Judy?\N- [Judy's voice] {\i1}You can go now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:10:13.54.1:10:15.13.Default..0.0.0..[groans]
Dialogue: 0.1:10:22.30.1:10:25.43.Default..0.0.0..[creaking]
Dialogue: 0.1:10:25.51.1:10:29.43.Default..0.0.0..[metal squeaking]
Dialogue: 0.1:10:31.81.1:10:35.44.Default..0.0.0..[squeaks]
Dialogue: 0.1:10:40.45.1:10:41.78.Default..0.0.0..[bang]
Dialogue: 0.1:10:44.53.1:10:46.87.Default..0.0.0..[whoosh]
Dialogue: 0.1:10:46.95.1:10:48.75.Default..0.0.0..[priest panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:10:51.16.1:10:54.96.Default..0.0.0..- [gasping]\N- [growling]
Dialogue: 0.1:10:55.54.1:10:57.80.Default..0.0.0..I am protected by God Almighty.
Dialogue: 0.1:10:59.46.1:11:03.84.Default..0.0.0..maker of heaven and Earth.\Nof all that is seen and unseen.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:03.93.1:11:05.76.Default..0.0.0..[roars]
Dialogue: 0.1:11:05.85.1:11:07.43.Default..0.0.0..My faith is my armor.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:07.81.1:11:09.10.Default..0.0.0..God's light…
Dialogue: 0.1:11:11.31.1:11:13.52.Default..0.0.0..God protect me!
Dialogue: 0.1:11:13.60.1:11:15.56.Default..0.0.0..[shouts]
Dialogue: 0.1:11:16.36.1:11:17.73.Default..0.0.0..[gasps. cries]
Dialogue: 0.1:11:20.36.1:11:22.20.Default..0.0.0..[inhales]
Dialogue: 0.1:11:36.58.1:11:38.55.Default..0.0.0..[hissing]
Dialogue: 0.1:11:38.63.1:11:40.09.Default..0.0.0..[revs]
Dialogue: 0.1:11:40.59.1:11:41.63.Default..0.0.0..[Tony] There she is!
Dialogue: 0.1:11:42.22.1:11:45.05.Default..0.0.0..See. you've always gotta check\Nif she's got a spark.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:45.14.1:11:46.72.Default..0.0.0..- [engine slows]\N- Ah.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:48.51.1:11:51.81.Default..0.0.0..Kept thinking it was the carburetor.\NShould have checked the spark plug.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:51.89.1:11:53.27.Default..0.0.0..[scoffs]
Dialogue: 0.1:11:53.98.1:11:55.19.Default..0.0.0..Nice work.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:55.27.1:11:56.56.Default..0.0.0..[Tony] Well. you know. I. uh.
Dialogue: 0.1:11:56.65.1:11:59.48.Default..0.0.0..I couldn't afford a mechanic in college.\Nso I had to teach myself.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:02.49.1:12:05.03.Default..0.0.0..Hey. how much has Judy told you\Nabout what we do?
Dialogue: 0.1:12:06.61.1:12:08.78.Default..0.0.0..Enough to not ask many questions.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:11.91.1:12:14.33.Default..0.0.0..Come inside. I wanna show you something.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:17.92.1:12:19.42.Default..0.0.0..Don't touch anything.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:21.21.1:12:25.18.Default..0.0.0..Everything you see in here\Nis either haunted. cursed.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:25.26.1:12:28.22.Default..0.0.0..or been used in some\Nsort of ritualistic practice.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:30.31.1:12:31.68.Default..0.0.0..Nothing's a toy.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:32.97.1:12:34.31.Default..0.0.0..Not even the toys.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:34.39.1:12:37.06.Default..0.0.0..- [Tony scoffs]\N- [Ed chuckles]
Dialogue: 0.1:12:39.02.1:12:41.02.Default..0.0.0..[Tony] If all these things are so evil.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:41.90.1:12:43.65.Default..0.0.0..why do you keep them around?
Dialogue: 0.1:12:43.74.1:12:45.45.Default..0.0.0..Why not just destroy them?
Dialogue: 0.1:12:45.53.1:12:48.99.Default..0.0.0..It's complicated.\NSometimes that makes things worse.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:49.53.1:12:52.83.Default..0.0.0..Sometimes… they just won't let you.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:54.04.1:12:56.54.Default..0.0.0..We've found it safer\Nto keep the genie in the bottle.
Dialogue: 0.1:12:57.67.1:12:59.42.Default..0.0.0..It's better in here than out there.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:00.42.1:13:01.80.Default..0.0.0..How many cases you guys had?
Dialogue: 0.1:13:01.88.1:13:03.55.Default..0.0.0..[Ed] Cases? Oh. [sighs]
Dialogue: 0.1:13:04.55.1:13:05.72.Default..0.0.0..Maybe a thousand?
Dialogue: 0.1:13:06.30.1:13:07.30.Default..0.0.0..A thousand?
Dialogue: 0.1:13:07.38.1:13:11.26.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. well. We started young.\Nabout your age.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:13.72.1:13:16.31.Default..0.0.0..Mmm. It's funny. This room.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:17.73.1:13:19.56.Default..0.0.0..every little thing in it…
Dialogue: 0.1:13:21.15.1:13:22.65.Default..0.0.0..…is our story.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:25.57.1:13:27.24.Default..0.0.0..It's our life's work.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:29.41.1:13:31.91.Default..0.0.0..Listen. the other day?
Dialogue: 0.1:13:32.95.1:13:34.04.Default..0.0.0..I get it.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:34.12.1:13:39.00.Default..0.0.0..Yeah I-- I was just… nervous.\Nand you're kinda intimidating.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:39.08.1:13:40.71.Default..0.0.0..[Ed] We almost lost Judy.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:43.21.1:13:44.67.Default..0.0.0..She was stillborn.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:48.38.1:13:49.84.Default..0.0.0..For probably a minute.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:53.26.1:13:55.77.Default..0.0.0..It was the longest minute of our lives.
Dialogue: 0.1:13:57.93.1:14:01.48.Default..0.0.0..And as a parent.\Nthat's something you never forget.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:05.07.1:14:06.90.Default..0.0.0..So. while I know she's your fiancée.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:09.57.1:14:10.70.Default..0.0.0..for us.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:11.41.1:14:15.95.Default..0.0.0..she will always be that little baby.\Nfighting for her life.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:18.71.1:14:20.12.Default..0.0.0..I understand. sir.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:23.17.1:14:24.38.Default..0.0.0..Do you?
Dialogue: 0.1:14:25.80.1:14:29.05.Default..0.0.0..[tapping]
Dialogue: 0.1:14:30.01.1:14:32.26.Default..0.0.0..- [panting]\N- [Ed] What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0.1:14:33.26.1:14:35.18.Default..0.0.0..- [Lorraine sighs]\N- What?
Dialogue: 0.1:14:36.01.1:14:39.98.Default..0.0.0..Father Gordon. he was a good man.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:41.73.1:14:43.15.Default..0.0.0..A man of God.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:44.56.1:14:46.73.Default..0.0.0..And he helped so many people.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:47.48.1:14:50.61.Default..0.0.0..I didn't know Father\Nto be a man of despair.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:51.40.1:14:54.70.Default..0.0.0..No. Father Gordon was light.
Dialogue: 0.1:14:57.04.1:15:00.29.Default..0.0.0..And he brought that light\Nto me and my family.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:00.37.1:15:02.83.Default..0.0.0..when we needed him most. [crying]
Dialogue: 0.1:15:04.88.1:15:06.17.Default..0.0.0..[inhales]
Dialogue: 0.1:15:07.63.1:15:10.22.Default..0.0.0..I only wish that… [sniffles]
Dialogue: 0.1:15:10.30.1:15:12.38.Default..0.0.0..…we could've done the same for him.
Dialogue: 0.1:15:12.93.1:15:14.64.Default..0.0.0..[sniffles]
Dialogue: 0.1:15:20.18.1:15:21.89.Default..0.0.0..[sniffles]
Dialogue: 0.1:15:23.85.1:15:25.65.Default..0.0.0..[exhales]
Dialogue: 0.1:15:52.97.1:15:55.93.Default..0.0.0..[deep rumble. creaking]
Dialogue: 0.1:15:56.97.1:15:59.18.Default..0.0.0..[growl]
Dialogue: 0.1:16:01.27.1:16:04.48.Default..0.0.0..[demonic exhale]
Dialogue: 0.1:16:12.86.1:16:14.45.Default..0.0.0..[Judy sighs]
Dialogue: 0.1:16:22.70.1:16:25.54.Default..0.0.0..Mr. Warren? Mrs. Warren?
Dialogue: 0.1:16:26.12.1:16:27.13.Default..0.0.0..[Ed] Yes?
Dialogue: 0.1:16:28.04.1:16:31.38.Default..0.0.0..I'm sorry. we never met.\NMy name is Father Ziegler.
Dialogue: 0.1:16:32.51.1:16:37.09.Default..0.0.0..You're actually both a bit infamous\Nwithin certain circles of the church.
Dialogue: 0.1:16:37.64.1:16:39.30.Default..0.0.0..Yes. we're aware.
Dialogue: 0.1:16:39.39.1:16:41.68.Default..0.0.0..But Gordon always spoke highly of you.
Dialogue: 0.1:16:41.76.1:16:45.35.Default..0.0.0..He believed in the mission.\NAnd the things you did together.
Dialogue: 0.1:16:45.44.1:16:47.35.Default..0.0.0..He considered you both friends.
Dialogue: 0.1:16:47.44.1:16:48.56.Default..0.0.0..Thank you. Father.
Dialogue: 0.1:16:52.98.1:16:54.24.Default..0.0.0..[engine starts]
Dialogue: 0.1:16:54.32.1:16:56.24.Default..0.0.0..Excuse me. Father.
Dialogue: 0.1:16:56.86.1:16:57.86.Default..0.0.0..Yes?
Dialogue: 0.1:16:57.95.1:16:59.45.Default..0.0.0..Mm.
Dialogue: 0.1:17:00.24.1:17:01.66.Default..0.0.0..Where was it?
Dialogue: 0.1:17:02.45.1:17:04.75.Default..0.0.0..Where did he die?
Dialogue: 0.1:17:05.91.1:17:07.25.Default..0.0.0..Pennsylvania.
Dialogue: 0.1:17:08.33.1:17:10.42.Default..0.0.0..God only knows why he was out there.
Dialogue: 0.1:17:16.72.1:17:19.26.Default..0.0.0..[plates clatter]
Dialogue: 0.1:17:29.69.1:17:32.07.Default..0.0.0..[inhales]
Dialogue: 0.1:17:43.58.1:17:45.58.Default..0.0.0..[disposal hums. creaks]
Dialogue: 0.1:17:47.12.1:17:48.58.Default..0.0.0..[power stops. starts]
Dialogue: 0.1:17:49.71.1:17:50.42.Default..0.0.0..[whispers] What?
Dialogue: 0.1:18:01.09.1:18:03.55.Default..0.0.0..[exhales. sighs]
Dialogue: 0.1:18:07.98.1:18:09.35.Default..0.0.0..[clink]
Dialogue: 0.1:18:18.78.1:18:24.62.Default..0.0.0..[young Judy]\N{\i1}♪ Lucy Locket lost her pocket ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:18:25.87.1:18:31.12.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}♪ Kitty Fisher found it ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:18:34.04.1:18:35.42.Default..0.0.0..[inhales]
Dialogue: 0.1:18:42.89.1:18:46.47.Default..0.0.0..[discordant choir vocalizing]
Dialogue: 0.1:18:51.77.1:18:52.44.Default..0.0.0..[shrieks]
Dialogue: 0.1:18:52.52.1:18:54.31.Default..0.0.0..Lorraine. What? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0.1:18:54.40.1:18:56.44.Default..0.0.0..[gasping]
Dialogue: 0.1:18:56.52.1:18:57.82.Default..0.0.0..[groans]
Dialogue: 0.1:18:57.90.1:18:59.61.Default..0.0.0..It's Judy.
Dialogue: 0.1:18:59.69.1:19:01.36.Default..0.0.0..There's something wrong with Judy.
Dialogue: 0.1:19:02.36.1:19:04.16.Default..0.0.0..[knocking]
Dialogue: 0.1:19:05.49.1:19:07.49.Default..0.0.0..[knocking]
Dialogue: 0.1:19:10.00.1:19:11.75.Default..0.0.0..[panting] Where is she?
Dialogue: 0.1:19:15.71.1:19:19.76.Default..0.0.0..- [vehicle hums]\N- [wind whistles]
Dialogue: 0.1:19:30.39.1:19:35.15.Default..0.0.0..[engine rumbles. stops]
Dialogue: 0.1:19:35.23.1:19:36.56.Default..0.0.0..Oh. boy.
Dialogue: 0.1:19:38.02.1:19:40.53.Default..0.0.0..[chattering]
Dialogue: 0.1:19:40.61.1:19:42.32.Default..0.0.0..[woman] Ma'am.\Ncan I ask you a few questions?
Dialogue: 0.1:19:47.24.1:19:50.37.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}Hey. stay back from here. okay?
Dialogue: 0.1:19:51.25.1:19:52.83.Default..0.0.0..Whatever is going on in that house.
Dialogue: 0.1:19:52.91.1:19:55.79.Default..0.0.0..we are getting Judy.\Nand we are taking her home.
Dialogue: 0.1:19:58.38.1:20:00.30.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}[Ed] All right. Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:01.09.1:20:02.42.Default..0.0.0..Sorry. Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:02.51.1:20:05.72.Default..0.0.0..[chatter]
Dialogue: 0.1:20:05.80.1:20:08.30.Default..0.0.0..[reporter] It's Ed and Lorraine Warren.\NMrs. Warren. what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0.1:20:08.39.1:20:10.10.Default..0.0.0..Mrs. Warren. have you been called in\Nfor reinforcements?
Dialogue: 0.1:20:10.18.1:20:11.18.Default..0.0.0..[man] What's in the house?
Dialogue: 0.1:20:11.27.1:20:14.14.Default..0.0.0..[reporter] Mr. Warren. will you\Nbe performing an exorcism today?
Dialogue: 0.1:20:14.23.1:20:15.02.Default..0.0.0..[Tony] Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:15.10.1:20:16.02.Default..0.0.0..[man] Are the Smurls hiding something?
Dialogue: 0.1:20:16.10.1:20:18.02.Default..0.0.0..- Do you know the Smurls?\N- [man] Ed and Lorraine!
Dialogue: 0.1:20:18.11.1:20:19.32.Default..0.0.0..[reporter] Are you coming out\Nof retirement?
Dialogue: 0.1:20:19.40.1:20:20.23.Default..0.0.0..[chatter]
Dialogue: 0.1:20:20.32.1:20:20.98.Default..0.0.0..[man] Sir?
Dialogue: 0.1:20:21.07.1:20:22.40.Default..0.0.0..- Sir. can you tell us your name?\N- [Tony] Hey. just back off.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:22.49.1:20:24.53.Default..0.0.0..[man] What's your connection\Nto the Warrens. sir?
Dialogue: 0.1:20:24.61.1:20:26.03.Default..0.0.0..Ed and Lorraine…
Dialogue: 0.1:20:26.11.1:20:27.37.Default..0.0.0..[knocking]
Dialogue: 0.1:20:27.45.1:20:29.58.Default..0.0.0..- You okay?\N- [chatter continues]
Dialogue: 0.1:20:31.49.1:20:33.16.Default..0.0.0..- [crowd clamoring]\N- Mr. Smurl?
Dialogue: 0.1:20:34.12.1:20:35.25.Default..0.0.0..Ed Warren.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:35.33.1:20:36.79.Default..0.0.0..Uh. yeah. This is my wife.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:36.87.1:20:39.88.Default..0.0.0..Lorraine. Yes. yes!\NPlease. come in. Please.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:40.71.1:20:42.42.Default..0.0.0..Oh. thank you so much for coming.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:42.51.1:20:45.17.Default..0.0.0..- We hear you're the experts.\N- [rumbling]
Dialogue: 0.1:20:45.26.1:20:47.22.Default..0.0.0..[Jack] People told us you were retired.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:48.89.1:20:49.93.Default..0.0.0..Well.
Dialogue: 0.1:20:51.01.1:20:53.02.Default..0.0.0..[disembodied whispering]
Dialogue: 0.1:20:54.43.1:20:57.90.Default..0.0.0..[female voice] {\i1}I'm so sorry.{\i0}\N{\i1}We're looking for our daughter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:20:58.44.1:20:59.73.Default..0.0.0..- [Judy] Mom?\N- [low snarl]
Dialogue: 0.1:20:59.81.1:21:00.82.Default..0.0.0..Mom?
Dialogue: 0.1:21:01.48.1:21:04.65.Default..0.0.0..[gasps] Judy! [panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:21:04.74.1:21:06.90.Default..0.0.0..That is Janet a-and Jack Smurl.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:07.49.1:21:09.20.Default..0.0.0..Thank God you're safe.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:10.74.1:21:13.04.Default..0.0.0..What are you doing out here?\NThis is not like you.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:13.12.1:21:16.25.Default..0.0.0..Father Gordon was here.\NHe came here just before he died.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:16.33.1:21:18.54.Default..0.0.0..I put two and two together.\Nand I found them.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:18.62.1:21:20.75.Default..0.0.0..- It's been going on for months.\N- We need to go.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:20.84.1:21:23.21.Default..0.0.0..What? No. Mom. Mom.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:23.30.1:21:25.17.Default..0.0.0..I'm so sorry. Ed. we need to go.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:25.26.1:21:26.59.Default..0.0.0..- You're leaving?\N- Yes. we're leaving.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:26.67.1:21:27.59.Default..0.0.0..Wait. what?
Dialogue: 0.1:21:27.68.1:21:28.93.Default..0.0.0..Really sorry if we've intruded.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:29.01.1:21:30.30.Default..0.0.0..- We can't leave!\N- We can't stay.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:30.39.1:21:31.43.Default..0.0.0..- We can talk about this outside.\N- Mom!
Dialogue: 0.1:21:31.51.1:21:32.51.Default..0.0.0..It's been a long drive.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:32.60.1:21:34.35.Default..0.0.0..Again. we're really sorry. Come on. Judy.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:34.43.1:21:36.35.Default..0.0.0..- [mom] Say something.\N- Stop!
Dialogue: 0.1:21:38.14.1:21:40.61.Default..0.0.0..[shuddering breathing]
Dialogue: 0.1:21:42.57.1:21:46.15.Default..0.0.0..[voice breaking]\NWe don't run from fights. right?
Dialogue: 0.1:21:47.90.1:21:49.66.Default..0.0.0..I mean. that's what\Nyou'd always tell each other.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:49.74.1:21:51.95.Default..0.0.0..when there was a family\Nthat needed you.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:54.79.1:21:58.50.Default..0.0.0..As a kid. I didn't understand\Nwhy you had to leave.
Dialogue: 0.1:21:59.37.1:22:02.75.Default..0.0.0..Why you gave so much of yourselves\Nto people you didn't know.
Dialogue: 0.1:22:04.30.1:22:06.09.Default..0.0.0..And even now. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0.1:22:07.26.1:22:08.55.Default..0.0.0..[stammers]
Dialogue: 0.1:22:08.63.1:22:11.64.Default..0.0.0..I don't know why I'm here. I really don't.
Dialogue: 0.1:22:12.51.1:22:14.26.Default..0.0.0..But we're all here now.
Dialogue: 0.1:22:15.64.1:22:18.31.Default..0.0.0..And they need us.
Dialogue: 0.1:22:29.82.1:22:31.70.Default..0.0.0..They need you.
Dialogue: 0.1:22:45.04.1:22:47.21.Default..0.0.0..{\an8}[crowd clamoring]
Dialogue: 0.1:22:49.92.1:22:50.97.Default..0.0.0..[grunts]
Dialogue: 0.1:23:00.85.1:23:03.44.Default..0.0.0..[indistinct chatter]
Dialogue: 0.1:23:05.19.1:23:06.11.Default..0.0.0..Any comments for us?
Dialogue: 0.1:23:06.19.1:23:08.73.Default..0.0.0..[reporter] Mr. Warren. do\Nyou think it's a real haunting?
Dialogue: 0.1:23:11.61.1:23:13.70.Default..0.0.0..We should have never gone to the press.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:13.78.1:23:16.20.Default..0.0.0..Now our neighbors can't stand us.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:16.28.1:23:18.08.Default..0.0.0..They think we wanted this.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:18.87.1:23:21.16.Default..0.0.0..I didn't know\Nit was gonna turn into a circus.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:21.25.1:23:23.67.Default..0.0.0..We wanted someone like you. experts.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:23.75.1:23:25.13.Default..0.0.0..People who've dealt with this before.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:25.21.1:23:28.42.Default..0.0.0..L-Let's… take this back\Nto the beginning. When did it start?
Dialogue: 0.1:23:28.50.1:23:31.09.Default..0.0.0..- Uh. Heather's confirmation.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:31.17.1:23:33.18.Default..0.0.0..What do you mean. you saw him die?
Dialogue: 0.1:23:33.51.1:23:34.51.Default..0.0.0..[shushes]
Dialogue: 0.1:23:35.97.1:23:37.30.Default..0.0.0..I mean. were you here?
Dialogue: 0.1:23:37.39.1:23:40.31.Default..0.0.0..No. back home. In a vision.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:40.39.1:23:42.85.Default..0.0.0..But… it was different.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:42.94.1:23:43.94.Default..0.0.0..Did you tell your mom?
Dialogue: 0.1:23:44.02.1:23:47.57.Default..0.0.0..No. I can't talk to her anymore.\NShe's always so…
Dialogue: 0.1:23:48.32.1:23:50.23.Default..0.0.0..- Worried.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:51.40.1:23:52.82.Default..0.0.0..There's something else.
Dialogue: 0.1:23:53.32.1:23:56.24.Default..0.0.0..I don't know how to say it.\Nbut it's like…
Dialogue: 0.1:23:57.95.1:24:02.71.Default..0.0.0..…something wants me to be here.
Dialogue: 0.1:24:04.25.1:24:07.08.Default..0.0.0..So your parents were living here?
Dialogue: 0.1:24:07.17.1:24:08.84.Default..0.0.0..Which one of you? Which parents?
Dialogue: 0.1:24:09.67.1:24:13.17.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. they've been with us all along.\Nsince we moved in. and um…
Dialogue: 0.1:24:55.67.1:24:57.68.Default..0.0.0..[lullaby playing]
Dialogue: 0.1:25:16.99.1:25:17.91.Default..0.0.0..[music stops]
Dialogue: 0.1:25:36.84.1:25:38.55.Default..0.0.0..[Simon panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:25:38.93.1:25:40.93.Default..0.0.0..He started making pancakes.
Dialogue: 0.1:25:42.85.1:25:43.72.Default..0.0.0..[Tony grunts]
Dialogue: 0.1:25:46.23.1:25:49.31.Default..0.0.0..So. is this. like. a normal case?
Dialogue: 0.1:25:50.31.1:25:52.52.Default..0.0.0..[chuckles] They're never normal.
Dialogue: 0.1:25:53.15.1:25:56.28.Default..0.0.0..No. I mean. do you always cook pancakes?
Dialogue: 0.1:25:56.36.1:25:58.74.Default..0.0.0..Is that part of the process?
Dialogue: 0.1:26:06.08.1:26:07.66.Default..0.0.0..Sometimes it's waffles.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:08.75.1:26:10.54.Default..0.0.0..[both laughing]
Dialogue: 0.1:26:13.04.1:26:15.30.Default..0.0.0..[Ed] No. every case is different.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:15.88.1:26:17.21.Default..0.0.0..Every family's different.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:18.17.1:26:21.51.Default..0.0.0..One thing that's always the same\Nis the fear.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:22.34.1:26:24.01.Default..0.0.0..You can see it in their eyes.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:25.35.1:26:27.22.Default..0.0.0..And a demon will prey on that.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:27.93.1:26:30.52.Default..0.0.0..It'll try to isolate them.\Nuse their fears against them.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:30.60.1:26:32.69.Default..0.0.0..So part of the job is just…
Dialogue: 0.1:26:34.11.1:26:35.90.Default..0.0.0..letting them know they're not alone.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:37.19.1:26:38.24.Default..0.0.0..Right.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:42.74.1:26:44.37.Default..0.0.0..Judy told me you were a cop.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:45.28.1:26:47.29.Default..0.0.0..What happened? Why'd you quit?
Dialogue: 0.1:26:47.37.1:26:48.37.Default..0.0.0..It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0.1:26:56.30.1:26:58.34.Default..0.0.0..Okay. so…
Dialogue: 0.1:26:59.51.1:27:00.51.Default..0.0.0..I was working in Bloomfield.
Dialogue: 0.1:27:01.72.1:27:04.22.Default..0.0.0..You know. small town.\NNothing ever happens.
Dialogue: 0.1:27:04.85.1:27:07.64.Default..0.0.0..Me and my partner.\Nwe get a domestic violence call.
Dialogue: 0.1:27:09.06.1:27:13.44.Default..0.0.0..And we pull up to the house.\Nand we hear fighting inside.
Dialogue: 0.1:27:13.52.1:27:15.94.Default..0.0.0..So. I knock on the door.
Dialogue: 0.1:27:16.77.1:27:18.03.Default..0.0.0..And immediately.
Dialogue: 0.1:27:18.11.1:27:20.15.Default..0.0.0..the door flies open.
Dialogue: 0.1:27:20.24.1:27:23.57.Default..0.0.0..and this guy shoves\Na twelve-gauge shotgun right in my face.
Dialogue: 0.1:27:24.95.1:27:27.33.Default..0.0.0..And I hear… click.
Dialogue: 0.1:27:28.49.1:27:29.83.Default..0.0.0..I. uh…
Dialogue: 0.1:27:30.33.1:27:33.92.Default..0.0.0..I unfreeze.\Nand. uh. we take the guy down.
Dialogue: 0.1:27:34.38.1:27:35.58.Default..0.0.0..Arrest him.
Dialogue: 0.1:27:37.63.1:27:40.26.Default..0.0.0..Later. my partner comes up to me.
Dialogue: 0.1:27:40.34.1:27:43.26.Default..0.0.0..and he says. "You're a dead man."
Dialogue: 0.1:27:45.01.1:27:46.35.Default..0.0.0..He shows me the shotgun.
Dialogue: 0.1:27:48.22.1:27:49.18.Default..0.0.0..It was loaded.
Dialogue: 0.1:27:50.52.1:27:52.39.Default..0.0.0..- Primer was struck on the shell.\N- [exhales]
Dialogue: 0.1:27:52.48.1:27:53.64.Default..0.0.0..Misfire.
Dialogue: 0.1:27:55.81.1:27:59.57.Default..0.0.0..I figure. there's a world where I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:01.11.1:28:03.61.Default..0.0.0..Where I never grow old.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:04.53.1:28:06.32.Default..0.0.0..I never have kids.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:06.95.1:28:08.99.Default..0.0.0..I never get to marry your daughter.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:14.67.1:28:17.63.Default..0.0.0..So next day. I-I quit.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:18.21.1:28:20.80.Default..0.0.0..and I go out and buy that ring for Judy.
Dialogue: 0.1:28:30.68.1:28:32.56.Default..0.0.0..[spatula scraping on pan]
Dialogue: 0.1:28:32.93.1:28:35.81.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- This is my wastepaper basket. Bert.{\i0}\N{\i1}- Of course. it's your waste basket!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:28:35.89.1:28:37.60.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- Oh. yeah.{\i0}\N{\i1}- You put it on my head!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:28:37.69.1:28:39.52.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- Thank you. Bert.{\i0}\N{\i1}- "Thank you?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:28:39.61.1:28:40.61.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}That's my wastepaper basket{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:28:40.69.1:28:42.57.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}for throwing stuff in{\i0}\N{\i1}when I make a mistake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:28:42.65.1:28:45.11.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Terrific. Okay. now. Ernie. Ernie…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:28:45.20.1:28:47.11.Default..0.0.0..[chatter on television]
Dialogue: 0.1:28:47.20.1:28:49.41.Default..0.0.0..[Judy] Should we do a silly face? Yeah?
Dialogue: 0.1:28:49.49.1:28:50.53.Default..0.0.0..[clicks]
Dialogue: 0.1:29:04.21.1:29:06.55.Default..0.0.0..Sorry. the flash was supposed to be off.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:06.63.1:29:08.59.Default..0.0.0..[flashbulb whines]
Dialogue: 0.1:29:09.85.1:29:11.47.Default..0.0.0..I just thought I could…
Dialogue: 0.1:29:13.31.1:29:14.73.Default..0.0.0..…document it all.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:19.15.1:29:20.23.Default..0.0.0..Everything okay?
Dialogue: 0.1:29:21.90.1:29:22.98.Default..0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:23.07.1:29:25.07.Default..0.0.0..[television chatter continues]
Dialogue: 0.1:29:30.57.1:29:34.29.Default..0.0.0..I just realized.\NI've never seen you guys at work.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:36.41.1:29:37.71.Default..0.0.0..[distant whisper]
Dialogue: 0.1:29:46.42.1:29:47.80.Default..0.0.0..I feel it. too.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:56.73.1:29:58.35.Default..0.0.0..- [inhales]\N- Stay here.
Dialogue: 0.1:29:58.44.1:30:01.11.Default..0.0.0..- Mom. I can help.\N- Judy. you promised.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:18.58.1:30:20.00.Default..0.0.0..[Susie] {\i1}Mommy. Mommy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:30:20.75.1:30:22.75.Default..0.0.0..[whirring]
Dialogue: 0.1:30:26.67.1:30:28.09.Default..0.0.0..[Susie] {\i1}Mommy. Mommy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:30:34.68.1:30:36.10.Default..0.0.0..[Susie] {\i1}Mommy. Mommy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:30:39.18.1:30:41.19.Default..0.0.0..[whirring]
Dialogue: 0.1:30:43.73.1:30:44.73.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Mommy--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:30:49.49.1:30:50.61.Default..0.0.0..- [shoe squeaks]\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 0.1:30:51.53.1:30:53.37.Default..0.0.0..[nervous laugh] Hey. Carin.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:53.45.1:30:54.45.Default..0.0.0..Sorry.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:54.53.1:30:55.45.Default..0.0.0..[Judy] It's okay.
Dialogue: 0.1:30:56.66.1:30:58.29.Default..0.0.0..Uh. what's her name?
Dialogue: 0.1:30:58.87.1:31:00.00.Default..0.0.0..This is Susie.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:00.79.1:31:02.08.Default..0.0.0..Hey. Susie.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:03.33.1:31:04.92.Default..0.0.0..Do you like dolls?
Dialogue: 0.1:31:05.54.1:31:06.92.Default..0.0.0..Uh…
Dialogue: 0.1:31:08.30.1:31:09.46.Default..0.0.0..Not really.
Dialogue: 0.1:31:40.79.1:31:42.41.Default..0.0.0..[bedsprings creak]
Dialogue: 0.1:31:53.43.1:31:55.43.Default..0.0.0..[bedsprings creak]
Dialogue: 0.1:32:00.43.1:32:01.43.Default..0.0.0..[sharp inhale]
Dialogue: 0.1:32:22.29.1:32:24.25.Default..0.0.0..[door opens]
Dialogue: 0.1:32:24.33.1:32:25.62.Default..0.0.0..[creak]
Dialogue: 0.1:32:28.29.1:32:30.30.Default..0.0.0..[door groaning]
Dialogue: 0.1:32:35.38.1:32:37.14.Default..0.0.0..[thud]
Dialogue: 0.1:32:38.35.1:32:39.35.Default..0.0.0..- [voices overlapping]\N- [woman] {\i1}Get away from her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:32:39.43.1:32:42.43.Default..0.0.0..[man] {\i1}I know what you did.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:32:42.52.1:32:43.98.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}You dirty girl!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:32:44.06.1:32:45.98.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- You filthy girl!{\i0}\N- [echoing scream]
Dialogue: 0.1:32:46.73.1:32:48.48.Default..0.0.0..[groaning sobs]
Dialogue: 0.1:32:48.56.1:32:49.82.Default..0.0.0..[woman] {\i1}No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:32:50.23.1:32:52.23.Default..0.0.0..[voices crescendo. fade]
Dialogue: 0.1:33:05.12.1:33:07.50.Default..0.0.0..The spirits. there are three of them.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:08.63.1:33:11.92.Default..0.0.0..They never lived in this house.\Nbut on this land.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:13.88.1:33:15.42.Default..0.0.0..This was farmland.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:18.97.1:33:20.18.Default..0.0.0..Uh…
Dialogue: 0.1:33:22.22.1:33:23.89.Default..0.0.0..There was a woman.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:24.77.1:33:27.02.Default..0.0.0..She was wild. She…
Dialogue: 0.1:33:28.31.1:33:30.02.Default..0.0.0..Just so tormented.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:30.81.1:33:33.40.Default..0.0.0..She had an affair. and…
Dialogue: 0.1:33:34.65.1:33:37.20.Default..0.0.0..…her husband went insane.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:38.24.1:33:41.28.Default..0.0.0..He took an axe. and he went after her.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:41.37.1:33:45.08.Default..0.0.0..She hid in the basement.\Nbut she wasn't alone.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:45.16.1:33:47.54.Default..0.0.0..She went with her elderly mother.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:49.96.1:33:52.75.Default..0.0.0..- And he killed them both.\N- Look. we've seen
Dialogue: 0.1:33:52.84.1:33:55.01.Default..0.0.0..violent manifestations like that before.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:55.09.1:33:56.67.Default..0.0.0..So why is this different?
Dialogue: 0.1:33:56.76.1:33:58.97.Default..0.0.0..The three spirits are a façade.
Dialogue: 0.1:33:59.26.1:34:01.93.Default..0.0.0..Something else is blocking my vision.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:02.85.1:34:04.35.Default..0.0.0..Hiding behind them.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:05.27.1:34:06.39.Default..0.0.0..Demonic?
Dialogue: 0.1:34:08.10.1:34:11.77.Default..0.0.0..It's controlling the spirits.\NIt's using them against the Smurls.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:11.86.1:34:15.82.Default..0.0.0..But what's it want?\NI mean. this has been going on for months.
Dialogue: 0.1:34:16.78.1:34:18.24.Default..0.0.0..What's it waiting for?
Dialogue: 0.1:34:24.66.1:34:25.49.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine's voice] Judy!
Dialogue: 0.1:34:28.08.1:34:29.25.Default..0.0.0..Mom?
Dialogue: 0.1:34:29.33.1:34:30.92.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine's voice]\NCan you come up here. please?
Dialogue: 0.1:34:53.81.1:34:54.94.Default..0.0.0..Mom?
Dialogue: 0.1:35:09.62.1:35:11.16.Default..0.0.0..[exhales]
Dialogue: 0.1:35:20.92.1:35:23.72.Default..0.0.0..[creaking footsteps on ladder]
Dialogue: 0.1:35:37.73.1:35:40.49.Default..0.0.0..[clicks]
Dialogue: 0.1:35:47.99.1:35:50.25.Default..0.0.0..[sighs]
Dialogue: 0.1:36:13.69.1:36:16.02.Default..0.0.0..- [rattles]\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 0.1:36:37.88.1:36:39.88.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:36:40.30.1:36:42.30.Default..0.0.0..[rumbling]
Dialogue: 0.1:36:53.18.1:36:54.98.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:37:01.90.1:37:04.61.Default..0.0.0..[scratching on glass]
Dialogue: 0.1:37:04.69.1:37:06.49.Default..0.0.0..[stops]
Dialogue: 0.1:37:06.57.1:37:07.57.Default..0.0.0..Oh.
Dialogue: 0.1:37:08.24.1:37:09.12.Default..0.0.0..[rattle]
Dialogue: 0.1:37:09.70.1:37:10.58.Default..0.0.0..[Judy gasps]
Dialogue: 0.1:37:13.95.1:37:15.16.Default..0.0.0..[exhales]
Dialogue: 0.1:37:16.16.1:37:18.08.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:37:27.09.1:37:27.76.Default..0.0.0..[gasps]
Dialogue: 0.1:37:28.80.1:37:30.22.Default..0.0.0..[whispers] Annabelle?
Dialogue: 0.1:37:39.19.1:37:40.23.Default..0.0.0..[creak]
Dialogue: 0.1:37:46.15.1:37:49.53.Default..0.0.0..- [scuttling]\N- [gasping. panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:37:54.70.1:37:56.62.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:37:56.91.1:37:57.83.Default..0.0.0..[Carin's voice] Judy?
Dialogue: 0.1:38:00.17.1:38:01.17.Default..0.0.0..[Carin's voice] Are you there?
Dialogue: 0.1:38:02.13.1:38:03.21.Default..0.0.0..Carin?
Dialogue: 0.1:38:39.33.1:38:41.33.Default..0.0.0..[ragged breathing]
Dialogue: 0.1:38:44.88.1:38:46.21.Default..0.0.0..[gasps]
Dialogue: 0.1:38:49.88.1:38:51.97.Default..0.0.0..[joints crunching. popping]
Dialogue: 0.1:38:52.05.1:38:53.35.Default..0.0.0..[discordant piano plays]
Dialogue: 0.1:38:59.27.1:39:00.35.Default..0.0.0..[shrieks]
Dialogue: 0.1:39:00.48.1:39:01.98.Default..0.0.0..[gasping]
Dialogue: 0.1:39:04.36.1:39:06.11.Default..0.0.0..[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0.1:39:07.48.1:39:09.11.Default..0.0.0..[Judy hyperventilating]
Dialogue: 0.1:39:11.49.1:39:12.45.Default..0.0.0..[yelps]
Dialogue: 0.1:39:12.53.1:39:14.53.Default..0.0.0..[screaming]
Dialogue: 0.1:39:15.49.1:39:16.95.Default..0.0.0..- [Ed] Judy!\N- [Lorraine] Judy!
Dialogue: 0.1:39:17.83.1:39:19.33.Default..0.0.0..- [groans]\N- [Lorraine gasps]
Dialogue: 0.1:39:19.41.1:39:20.71.Default..0.0.0..Your head!
Dialogue: 0.1:39:20.79.1:39:22.83.Default..0.0.0..- What happened?\N- [Judy whimpers]
Dialogue: 0.1:39:25.21.1:39:27.09.Default..0.0.0..[Judy's breath catches]
Dialogue: 0.1:39:28.63.1:39:30.26.Default..0.0.0..There's something in the attic.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:39.47.1:39:40.89.Default..0.0.0..It can't be.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:41.73.1:39:45.94.Default..0.0.0..[exhales] It… found us.
Dialogue: 0.1:39:52.03.1:39:53.20.Default..0.0.0..Lorraine?
Dialogue: 0.1:39:58.95.1:40:01.16.Default..0.0.0..No. Lorraine. No. don't.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:15.26.1:40:18.43.Default..0.0.0..Ed. something's changed.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:20.97.1:40:22.93.Default..0.0.0..- Something's different.\N- [engine turns over]
Dialogue: 0.1:40:30.28.1:40:33.36.Default..0.0.0..[Ed] {\i1}Then. after about a week.{\i0}\N{\i1}Judy recovered.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:40:33.78.1:40:36.20.Default..0.0.0..The doctors said\Nthey'd never seen anything like it.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:37.32.1:40:39.08.Default..0.0.0..[sighs] She was a miracle.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:40.45.1:40:43.83.Default..0.0.0..But as for that mirror.\Nwe never saw it again…
Dialogue: 0.1:40:45.83.1:40:47.13.Default..0.0.0..…until today.
Dialogue: 0.1:40:48.25.1:40:51.59.Default..0.0.0..[Dawn] {\i1}But I don't understand.{\i0}\N{\i1}Heather and I threw that thing away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:40:51.67.1:40:54.80.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine] {\i1}With these things.{\i0}\N{\i1}it's never that simple.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:40:55.93.1:41:00.18.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}It wasn't done with you.{\i0}\N{\i1}and it wasn't done with us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:41:02.97.1:41:04.81.Default..0.0.0..Okay. so then what happened to the woman
Dialogue: 0.1:41:05.89.1:41:07.73.Default..0.0.0..from the antique store?
Dialogue: 0.1:41:11.32.1:41:12.28.Default..0.0.0..We don't know.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:12.65.1:41:13.86.Default..0.0.0..Uh…
Dialogue: 0.1:41:15.07.1:41:16.28.Default..0.0.0..We never went back.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:17.28.1:41:20.37.Default..0.0.0..That thing in your attic is a demon.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:20.70.1:41:22.91.Default..0.0.0..It's the first one\Nthat we ever encountered.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:24.12.1:41:28.67.Default..0.0.0..We were young. and we were scared.\Nand we almost lost our daughter.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:30.00.1:41:33.00.Default..0.0.0..So. we told ourselves that\Nthe risk was just too great.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:33.09.1:41:35.22.Default..0.0.0..so we couldn't chance going back.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:36.67.1:41:38.09.Default..0.0.0..So. yes.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:40.05.1:41:41.26.Default..0.0.0..We ran away.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:44.97.1:41:45.89.Default..0.0.0..[Jack] I'll…
Dialogue: 0.1:41:46.98.1:41:49.65.Default..0.0.0..…take it as a good sign\Nyou're still here.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:49.73.1:41:51.06.Default..0.0.0..Mm.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:51.15.1:41:52.32.Default..0.0.0..We're not leaving you.
Dialogue: 0.1:41:54.61.1:41:55.49.Default..0.0.0..[Judy coughs]
Dialogue: 0.1:41:55.57.1:41:57.36.Default..0.0.0..[hacking coughs]
Dialogue: 0.1:41:59.99.1:42:01.07.Default..0.0.0..[Judy clears her throat]
Dialogue: 0.1:42:01.16.1:42:01.99.Default..0.0.0..[Tony] Some water?
Dialogue: 0.1:42:02.49.1:42:03.62.Default..0.0.0..Sorry. [sniffles]
Dialogue: 0.1:42:04.49.1:42:05.33.Default..0.0.0..[Heather] So. what now?
Dialogue: 0.1:42:06.70.1:42:08.00.Default..0.0.0..How do you get rid of it?
Dialogue: 0.1:42:09.67.1:42:12.79.Default..0.0.0..Ed! You're really\Ngonna take that thing home?
Dialogue: 0.1:42:12.88.1:42:14.38.Default..0.0.0..We can't leave it here.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:14.46.1:42:16.92.Default..0.0.0..Artifact room is the only place\Nthat can contain it.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:20.80.1:42:24.89.Default..0.0.0..All right. West Pittston.\Nback home to Monroe. Take 80.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:24.97.1:42:27.31.Default..0.0.0..Lorraine and Judy can stay behind.\NWait. 84 is faster.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:27.39.1:42:29.23.Default..0.0.0..Eighty is much quicker this time of night.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:31.10.1:42:33.19.Default..0.0.0..Listen to me. whatever happens tonight.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:33.27.1:42:35.28.Default..0.0.0..you have got to do what I say. okay?
Dialogue: 0.1:42:36.32.1:42:37.15.Default..0.0.0..Got it.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:40.82.1:42:42.16.Default..0.0.0..[thunder rumbling]
Dialogue: 0.1:42:42.87.1:42:44.12.Default..0.0.0..What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0.1:42:48.33.1:42:49.29.Default..0.0.0..It's nothin'.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:50.33.1:42:51.29.Default..0.0.0..Everything okay?
Dialogue: 0.1:42:51.37.1:42:53.42.Default..0.0.0..I-It's just something Lorraine said.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:55.55.1:42:57.05.Default..0.0.0..Something feels different.
Dialogue: 0.1:42:58.76.1:43:00.38.Default..0.0.0..[thunder rumbles]
Dialogue: 0.1:43:02.09.1:43:03.26.Default..0.0.0..[coughing weakly]
Dialogue: 0.1:43:03.34.1:43:05.05.Default..0.0.0..[thunder rolling]
Dialogue: 0.1:43:09.89.1:43:12.19.Default..0.0.0..Mom. I'm-- I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:12.65.1:43:14.27.Default..0.0.0..No. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:15.15.1:43:17.36.Default..0.0.0..I should have never let you stay.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:22.70.1:43:25.28.Default..0.0.0..Once we start. there's no going back.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:26.62.1:43:27.74.Default..0.0.0..Don't look at it.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:29.20.1:43:31.75.Default..0.0.0..And don't touch it directly.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:32.50.1:43:33.92.Default..0.0.0..Just keep your gloves on.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:34.54.1:43:35.75.Default..0.0.0..Anything can happen.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:37.25.1:43:39.13.Default..0.0.0..And most likely. anything will.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:39.21.1:43:40.51.Default..0.0.0..[paper rustling]
Dialogue: 0.1:43:41.80.1:43:42.76.Default..0.0.0..[Ed sighs]
Dialogue: 0.1:43:45.22.1:43:46.72.Default..0.0.0.."St. Michael the Archangel.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:47.72.1:43:49.35.Default..0.0.0..defend us in the day of battle.
Dialogue: 0.1:43:50.48.1:43:53.52.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Be our safeguard against the wickedness{\i0}\N{\i1}and snares of the devil."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:43:53.60.1:43:54.94.Default..0.0.0..[coughing]
Dialogue: 0.1:43:55.81.1:43:57.02.Default..0.0.0..[Ed] {\i1}"May God rebuke him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:43:58.02.1:44:01.28.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}And by the power of God.{\i0}\N{\i1}cast into hell. Satan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:44:01.36.1:44:04.49.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}and all other evil spirits{\i0}\N{\i1}who prowl through the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:44:05.07.1:44:06.74.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}seeking the ruin of souls."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:44:06.82.1:44:08.45.Default..0.0.0..[ratchets]
Dialogue: 0.1:44:08.53.1:44:09.70.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- "Amen."{\i0}\N- [strap tightens]
Dialogue: 0.1:44:09.79.1:44:10.66.Default..0.0.0..[Ed grunts]
Dialogue: 0.1:44:11.00.1:44:12.16.Default..0.0.0..- I'll get the car ready.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:12.25.1:44:13.50.Default..0.0.0..- We'll be down in a second.\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:16.71.1:44:17.59.Default..0.0.0..- [strained] You ready?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:17.67.1:44:19.30.Default..0.0.0..Two. three… Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:19.38.1:44:20.71.Default..0.0.0..[Simon barking]
Dialogue: 0.1:44:20.80.1:44:22.30.Default..0.0.0..- [Dawn] Come on. Simon!\N- [Heather] Let's go. Simon!
Dialogue: 0.1:44:22.38.1:44:23.51.Default..0.0.0..[Dawn] Come on. Simon!
Dialogue: 0.1:44:23.59.1:44:25.18.Default..0.0.0..- Come on! Be a good boy.\N- Come on!
Dialogue: 0.1:44:25.26.1:44:27.01.Default..0.0.0..- Girls. get him outta here.\N- [barking]
Dialogue: 0.1:44:27.10.1:44:28.14.Default..0.0.0..We're trying!
Dialogue: 0.1:44:29.43.1:44:32.02.Default..0.0.0..So. is it just drywall\Nunderneath the insulation?
Dialogue: 0.1:44:32.48.1:44:33.14.Default..0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:33.73.1:44:35.19.Default..0.0.0..So. if we step off these boards.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:35.27.1:44:36.77.Default..0.0.0..- we're going--\N- Straight through the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:37.23.1:44:38.44.Default..0.0.0..Don't wanna make it too easy.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:38.52.1:44:40.82.Default..0.0.0..[thunder rumbles]
Dialogue: 0.1:44:40.90.1:44:42.90.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:44:44.49.1:44:46.24.Default..0.0.0..[thunder rolling]
Dialogue: 0.1:44:47.12.1:44:48.32.Default..0.0.0..[Jack] Is it just me or…
Dialogue: 0.1:44:49.53.1:44:51.20.Default..0.0.0..or does it feel like it's getting heavier?
Dialogue: 0.1:44:51.70.1:44:53.62.Default..0.0.0..[Ed] It is.\NSometimes these things can be…
Dialogue: 0.1:44:54.41.1:44:55.29.Default..0.0.0..- [Jack groans]\N- …stubborn.
Dialogue: 0.1:44:55.79.1:44:56.58.Default..0.0.0..Oh!
Dialogue: 0.1:44:57.63.1:44:58.29.Default..0.0.0..[Ed] You okay?
Dialogue: 0.1:45:00.17.1:45:01.21.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah. I'm good.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0.1:45:01.80.1:45:03.05.Default..0.0.0..[clicking]
Dialogue: 0.1:45:04.34.1:45:05.30.Default..0.0.0..Ed…
Dialogue: 0.1:45:06.72.1:45:07.39.Default..0.0.0..Look.
Dialogue: 0.1:45:11.60.1:45:12.56.Default..0.0.0..Keep moving.
Dialogue: 0.1:45:12.64.1:45:13.89.Default..0.0.0..[engine sputtering]
Dialogue: 0.1:45:15.94.1:45:17.27.Default..0.0.0..[sputtering continues]
Dialogue: 0.1:45:19.61.1:45:20.52.Default..0.0.0..Come on!
Dialogue: 0.1:45:20.61.1:45:22.57.Default..0.0.0..[coughing]
Dialogue: 0.1:45:22.65.1:45:25.57.Default..0.0.0..Judy… Judy. what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0.1:45:26.65.1:45:27.82.Default..0.0.0..[groans]
Dialogue: 0.1:45:31.66.1:45:32.49.Default..0.0.0..[whispering] Mom.
Dialogue: 0.1:45:32.58.1:45:33.58.Default..0.0.0..[gasps]
Dialogue: 0.1:45:36.37.1:45:37.87.Default..0.0.0..I don't feel good.
Dialogue: 0.1:45:38.46.1:45:39.83.Default..0.0.0..[men grunting]
Dialogue: 0.1:45:41.59.1:45:42.59.Default..0.0.0..We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0.1:45:42.67.1:45:44.26.Default..0.0.0..[clicking]
Dialogue: 0.1:45:50.85.1:45:52.39.Default..0.0.0..- [gasps]\N- Don't look at it!
Dialogue: 0.1:45:52.47.1:45:54.47.Default..0.0.0..- [Jack groans]\N- Don't-- don't look at it!
Dialogue: 0.1:45:54.97.1:45:56.10.Default..0.0.0..She's with us!
Dialogue: 0.1:45:56.18.1:45:57.10.Default..0.0.0..Jack. it's just us.
Dialogue: 0.1:45:57.44.1:45:58.94.Default..0.0.0..She's here! I saw her. Ed.
Dialogue: 0.1:45:59.02.1:46:00.27.Default..0.0.0..- I saw her.\N- No. it's just us.
Dialogue: 0.1:46:00.35.1:46:02.48.Default..0.0.0..- She is here. [whimpers]\N- Jack.
Dialogue: 0.1:46:02.57.1:46:04.44.Default..0.0.0..- Focus on what you're doing.\N- I saw her. She's here.
Dialogue: 0.1:46:04.73.1:46:05.86.Default..0.0.0..Jack. watch where you're going.
Dialogue: 0.1:46:05.94.1:46:06.86.Default..0.0.0..[Jack cries out]
Dialogue: 0.1:46:07.36.1:46:08.74.Default..0.0.0..Oh! [grunts]
Dialogue: 0.1:46:09.57.1:46:10.82.Default..0.0.0..[straining]
Dialogue: 0.1:46:10.91.1:46:12.91.Default..0.0.0..Jack. get outta the way! No!
Dialogue: 0.1:46:13.91.1:46:14.58.Default..0.0.0..[cries out]
Dialogue: 0.1:46:14.95.1:46:16.33.Default..0.0.0..- [Jack moaning]\N- [Carin] Daddy!
Dialogue: 0.1:46:16.41.1:46:18.83.Default..0.0.0..- [Jack moaning]\N- Stay right here.
Dialogue: 0.1:46:18.92.1:46:20.00.Default..0.0.0..Mommy!
Dialogue: 0.1:46:20.29.1:46:22.34.Default..0.0.0..Ed? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0.1:46:22.42.1:46:23.71.Default..0.0.0..Jack! What happened?
Dialogue: 0.1:46:23.80.1:46:25.71.Default..0.0.0..[straining] Get back!
Dialogue: 0.1:46:26.01.1:46:26.96.Default..0.0.0..No. get back!
Dialogue: 0.1:46:27.05.1:46:28.47.Default..0.0.0..Just keep everybody away.
Dialogue: 0.1:46:29.88.1:46:31.68.Default..0.0.0..- Let me go get Tony.\N- No. I can do this.
Dialogue: 0.1:46:31.76.1:46:33.01.Default..0.0.0..Just help me up.
Dialogue: 0.1:46:34.10.1:46:34.97.Default..0.0.0..- [groans]\N- [coughing]
Dialogue: 0.1:46:35.06.1:46:37.39.Default..0.0.0..[Ed] Lorraine. stay down there!\NKeep everybody down there.
Dialogue: 0.1:46:40.31.1:46:42.94.Default..0.0.0..[gasping. coughing]
Dialogue: 0.1:46:43.82.1:46:45.98.Default..0.0.0..- Come on. Come on.\N- [engine sputtering]
Dialogue: 0.1:46:47.78.1:46:48.99.Default..0.0.0..- [engine revs]\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0.1:46:51.28.1:46:53.28.Default..0.0.0..[tires screech]
Dialogue: 0.1:47:04.54.1:47:05.50.Default..0.0.0..What the--
Dialogue: 0.1:47:10.72.1:47:12.72.Default..0.0.0..Oh. man. Oh. God.
Dialogue: 0.1:47:14.64.1:47:15.93.Default..0.0.0..My God.
Dialogue: 0.1:47:18.31.1:47:19.64.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:47:19.73.1:47:20.48.Default..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.1:47:21.06.1:47:22.85.Default..0.0.0..[thunder rumbling]
Dialogue: 0.1:47:33.45.1:47:37.24.Default..0.0.0..[rain patters]
Dialogue: 0.1:47:49.05.1:47:51.42.Default..0.0.0..- [wind whistles]\N- [thunderclap]
Dialogue: 0.1:47:58.31.1:47:59.85.Default..0.0.0..[breathing shakily]
Dialogue: 0.1:48:00.47.1:48:02.48.Default..0.0.0..[lullaby playing faintly]
Dialogue: 0.1:48:26.83.1:48:28.84.Default..0.0.0..[lullaby tinkling. machinery whirring]
Dialogue: 0.1:48:35.47.1:48:36.43.Default..0.0.0..No.
Dialogue: 0.1:48:36.51.1:48:38.14.Default..0.0.0..[Judy coughing]
Dialogue: 0.1:48:41.60.1:48:43.60.Default..0.0.0..[singing] ♪ {\i1}Lucy Locket ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:48:44.52.1:48:46.77.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}♪ Lost her pocket ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:48:47.52.1:48:50.98.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}♪ Kitty Fisher found it ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:48:53.03.1:48:58.20.Default..0.0.0..[voice creaking]\N{\i1}♪ Not a penny was there in it ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:49:00.74.1:49:05.46.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}♪ Only ribbon 'round it ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:49:07.33.1:49:08.63.Default..0.0.0..Mommy?
Dialogue: 0.1:49:10.04.1:49:12.05.Default..0.0.0..I don't feel so good.
Dialogue: 0.1:49:12.13.1:49:13.55.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:49:13.63.1:49:14.55.Default..0.0.0..Judy?
Dialogue: 0.1:49:16.13.1:49:20.05.Default..0.0.0..[demonic voice]\NWe've been waiting so patiently
Dialogue: 0.1:49:20.14.1:49:24.02.Default..0.0.0..for little Judy to come back to us.
Dialogue: 0.1:49:24.48.1:49:26.48.Default..0.0.0..[snarling]
Dialogue: 0.1:49:28.10.1:49:29.36.Default..0.0.0..[screams]
Dialogue: 0.1:49:32.69.1:49:34.15.Default..0.0.0..[both men grunting]
Dialogue: 0.1:49:34.24.1:49:36.03.Default..0.0.0..- [Ed] It's okay.\N- [Jack] I'm sorry. Ed.
Dialogue: 0.1:49:36.11.1:49:36.99.Default..0.0.0..[Jack grunts]
Dialogue: 0.1:49:39.32.1:49:40.78.Default..0.0.0..[both panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:49:41.37.1:49:42.70.Default..0.0.0..Okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0.1:49:43.70.1:49:44.58.Default..0.0.0..Easy. easy. easy.
Dialogue: 0.1:49:44.66.1:49:46.46.Default..0.0.0..[Simon barking]
Dialogue: 0.1:49:46.75.1:49:48.71.Default..0.0.0..Simon. get back.
Dialogue: 0.1:49:51.38.1:49:53.09.Default..0.0.0..[Simon barking]
Dialogue: 0.1:49:54.42.1:49:55.13.Default..0.0.0..Judy?
Dialogue: 0.1:49:55.59.1:49:56.80.Default..0.0.0..- [Dawn] Simon. come back.\N- [barking]
Dialogue: 0.1:49:58.43.1:49:59.34.Default..0.0.0..[Tony] What's going on?
Dialogue: 0.1:50:00.01.1:50:01.22.Default..0.0.0..Girls. come.
Dialogue: 0.1:50:01.80.1:50:02.81.Default..0.0.0..Pull him. Heather!
Dialogue: 0.1:50:03.26.1:50:04.35.Default..0.0.0..[barking]
Dialogue: 0.1:50:04.43.1:50:05.85.Default..0.0.0..- [Carin] Mommy?\N- [Simon yelps]
Dialogue: 0.1:50:05.93.1:50:06.89.Default..0.0.0..[Simon whines]
Dialogue: 0.1:50:06.98.1:50:08.06.Default..0.0.0..No! No!
Dialogue: 0.1:50:08.77.1:50:09.73.Default..0.0.0..- [Shannon] Mommy!\N- Hey!
Dialogue: 0.1:50:10.86.1:50:11.61.Default..0.0.0..[yelps]
Dialogue: 0.1:50:11.69.1:50:12.94.Default..0.0.0..[twins screaming]
Dialogue: 0.1:50:14.82.1:50:15.48.Default..0.0.0..[grunts]
Dialogue: 0.1:50:15.57.1:50:16.82.Default..0.0.0..[twins sobbing]
Dialogue: 0.1:50:16.90.1:50:18.53.Default..0.0.0..- It's okay.\N- [Carin] Simon!
Dialogue: 0.1:50:18.61.1:50:19.74.Default..0.0.0..- Oh. no!\N- [Tony] Let me in!
Dialogue: 0.1:50:19.82.1:50:21.16.Default..0.0.0..- [Carin] Stop! No!\N- [Shannon] No!
Dialogue: 0.1:50:21.70.1:50:23.87.Default..0.0.0..- [Heather] Simon!\N- No! You get away from them!
Dialogue: 0.1:50:24.20.1:50:25.37.Default..0.0.0..[mom] You get away from them!
Dialogue: 0.1:50:25.45.1:50:26.20.Default..0.0.0..Judy.
Dialogue: 0.1:50:28.91.1:50:30.50.Default..0.0.0..No. No!
Dialogue: 0.1:50:30.58.1:50:33.29.Default..0.0.0..No. Judy. look at me.\NLook in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0.1:50:34.13.1:50:35.25.Default..0.0.0..[feebly] Daddy?
Dialogue: 0.1:50:35.34.1:50:36.05.Default..0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.1:50:36.84.1:50:38.13.Default..0.0.0..- [Tony] Come on. come on.\N- [twins yelling]
Dialogue: 0.1:50:38.47.1:50:39.72.Default..0.0.0..It's-- Judy--
Dialogue: 0.1:50:40.43.1:50:43.18.Default..0.0.0..- Open the door! Open the door!\N- Open the door!
Dialogue: 0.1:50:43.26.1:50:45.72.Default..0.0.0..- Open the door!\N- It won't open!
Dialogue: 0.1:50:46.39.1:50:49.48.Default..0.0.0..- [singing] {\i1}♪ Lucy Locket… ♪{\i0}\N- Judy. listen to my voice.
Dialogue: 0.1:50:49.56.1:50:52.56.Default..0.0.0..- I know you're in there. It's Daddy!\N{\i1}- ♪ …Lost her pocket ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:50:53.23.1:50:57.15.Default..0.0.0..[whispering] ♪ {\i1}Kitty Fisher found it {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.1:50:57.23.1:51:00.15.Default..0.0.0..I know you can hear me. Judy. Judy!
Dialogue: 0.1:51:00.24.1:51:02.53.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}You're not there {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.1:51:03.12.1:51:04.16.Default..0.0.0..[snarls]
Dialogue: 0.1:51:04.24.1:51:06.24.Default..0.0.0..- [heartbeat thudding]\N- [gasps]
Dialogue: 0.1:51:06.95.1:51:08.50.Default..0.0.0..[crying]
Dialogue: 0.1:51:08.58.1:51:10.08.Default..0.0.0..[sputtering]
Dialogue: 0.1:51:11.21.1:51:13.08.Default..0.0.0..[groaning]
Dialogue: 0.1:51:15.34.1:51:17.05.Default..0.0.0..- [grunts]\N- [wailing]
Dialogue: 0.1:51:19.63.1:51:20.72.Default..0.0.0..[grunts]
Dialogue: 0.1:51:22.09.1:51:22.97.Default..0.0.0..Judy.
Dialogue: 0.1:51:23.59.1:51:24.93.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:51:25.64.1:51:27.64.Default..0.0.0..[family screaming downstairs]
Dialogue: 0.1:51:28.85.1:51:31.64.Default..0.0.0..[singing] {\i1}♪ Lucy Locket… ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:51:32.90.1:51:34.36.Default..0.0.0..- [grunts]\N- Mommy!
Dialogue: 0.1:51:35.36.1:51:36.07.Default..0.0.0..No!
Dialogue: 0.1:51:36.15.1:51:37.82.Default..0.0.0..[straining]
Dialogue: 0.1:51:38.65.1:51:40.95.Default..0.0.0..Wait there!\NI'm going 'round the back. okay?
Dialogue: 0.1:51:42.45.1:51:43.95.Default..0.0.0..[thunder rumbling]
Dialogue: 0.1:51:47.28.1:51:48.08.Default..0.0.0..[groans]
Dialogue: 0.1:51:50.70.1:51:52.42.Default..0.0.0..[grunts]
Dialogue: 0.1:51:56.96.1:51:58.96.Default..0.0.0..[clunk. creak]
Dialogue: 0.1:52:01.13.1:52:03.13.Default..0.0.0..- [panting]\N- [heavy footfalls]
Dialogue: 0.1:52:15.27.1:52:19.15.Default..0.0.0..[ragged breath]
Dialogue: 0.1:52:23.11.1:52:24.32.Default..0.0.0..[shushes]
Dialogue: 0.1:52:25.61.1:52:26.78.Default..0.0.0..[gasps]
Dialogue: 0.1:52:26.87.1:52:28.45.Default..0.0.0..[creaking]
Dialogue: 0.1:52:35.12.1:52:37.13.Default..0.0.0..[blood splashing]
Dialogue: 0.1:52:38.50.1:52:39.59.Default..0.0.0..[gasps]
Dialogue: 0.1:52:39.67.1:52:40.80.Default..0.0.0..[ghostly snarl]
Dialogue: 0.1:52:40.88.1:52:41.76.Default..0.0.0..[boom]
Dialogue: 0.1:52:42.30.1:52:43.30.Default..0.0.0..[boom]
Dialogue: 0.1:52:43.63.1:52:44.51.Default..0.0.0..[boom]
Dialogue: 0.1:52:45.26.1:52:46.26.Default..0.0.0..Oh. God.
Dialogue: 0.1:52:49.68.1:52:50.97.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine cries out]
Dialogue: 0.1:52:51.06.1:52:53.27.Default..0.0.0..- [snarls]\N- [yelps]
Dialogue: 0.1:52:53.35.1:52:54.77.Default..0.0.0..[guttural snarling]
Dialogue: 0.1:52:55.35.1:52:56.19.Default..0.0.0..[bubbling]
Dialogue: 0.1:52:56.52.1:52:57.81.Default..0.0.0..[crying out]
Dialogue: 0.1:52:59.61.1:53:00.69.Default..0.0.0..[shouts]
Dialogue: 0.1:53:02.49.1:53:03.28.Default..0.0.0..[yelps]
Dialogue: 0.1:53:03.36.1:53:05.36.Default..0.0.0..[laughing cruelly]
Dialogue: 0.1:53:06.03.1:53:07.53.Default..0.0.0..- [yelps]\N- [laughter continues]
Dialogue: 0.1:53:10.12.1:53:11.29.Default..0.0.0..[cries out]
Dialogue: 0.1:53:11.37.1:53:12.54.Default..0.0.0..[snarls]
Dialogue: 0.1:53:12.62.1:53:13.83.Default..0.0.0..- [wails]\N- [roars]
Dialogue: 0.1:53:15.16.1:53:16.29.Default..0.0.0..- [whimpers. gasps]\N- [Tony] Lorraine?
Dialogue: 0.1:53:16.37.1:53:17.29.Default..0.0.0..[footsteps approaching]
Dialogue: 0.1:53:18.13.1:53:19.50.Default..0.0.0..Hey. you okay?
Dialogue: 0.1:53:19.59.1:53:21.59.Default..0.0.0..Tony. [gasps]
Dialogue: 0.1:53:22.76.1:53:24.88.Default..0.0.0..[Ed grunting. panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:53:26.01.1:53:27.64.Default..0.0.0..[wincing. grunting]
Dialogue: 0.1:53:28.59.1:53:30.05.Default..0.0.0..- Stay here! Stay here!\N- No!
Dialogue: 0.1:53:30.14.1:53:32.26.Default..0.0.0..[Carin] No. no. Mommy. don't leave us!
Dialogue: 0.1:53:32.35.1:53:33.27.Default..0.0.0..[pants. moans]
Dialogue: 0.1:53:33.35.1:53:34.43.Default..0.0.0..[twins sobbing]
Dialogue: 0.1:53:34.52.1:53:36.14.Default..0.0.0..[panting] Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0.1:53:36.23.1:53:37.10.Default..0.0.0..- [Ed panting]\N- What should I do?
Dialogue: 0.1:53:37.19.1:53:38.90.Default..0.0.0..Should I call the police? An ambulance?
Dialogue: 0.1:53:38.98.1:53:40.44.Default..0.0.0..- There's no time.\N- Mommy!
Dialogue: 0.1:53:40.52.1:53:41.90.Default..0.0.0..Get Jack and the girls.\Nand get outta here.
Dialogue: 0.1:53:41.98.1:53:42.65.Default..0.0.0..Jack?
Dialogue: 0.1:53:42.73.1:53:43.90.Default..0.0.0..She's going up to the attic.
Dialogue: 0.1:53:44.19.1:53:44.94.Default..0.0.0..[Jack] Go!
Dialogue: 0.1:53:45.36.1:53:46.20.Default..0.0.0..[crying]
Dialogue: 0.1:53:46.28.1:53:48.66.Default..0.0.0..[Jack] Come on. quickly. girls! Get out!
Dialogue: 0.1:53:48.74.1:53:50.87.Default..0.0.0..- [Janet] Let me help you!\N- [Heather] It's okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0.1:53:53.45.1:53:54.83.Default..0.0.0..Ed! [gasps]
Dialogue: 0.1:53:54.91.1:53:56.37.Default..0.0.0..It wanted Judy.
Dialogue: 0.1:53:56.91.1:53:58.62.Default..0.0.0..It's always been Judy.
Dialogue: 0.1:54:00.46.1:54:01.46.Default..0.0.0..Get the book!
Dialogue: 0.1:54:07.47.1:54:08.47.Default..0.0.0..It's all right.
Dialogue: 0.1:54:08.55.1:54:10.05.Default..0.0.0..- [Simon barking]\N- [girls sobbing]
Dialogue: 0.1:54:10.55.1:54:12.56.Default..0.0.0..[Simon barking]
Dialogue: 0.1:54:20.35.1:54:22.31.Default..0.0.0..[Judy choking]
Dialogue: 0.1:54:24.15.1:54:25.73.Default..0.0.0..[guttural gasping]
Dialogue: 0.1:54:26.28.1:54:27.03.Default..0.0.0..Judy!
Dialogue: 0.1:54:27.61.1:54:28.95.Default..0.0.0..[grunting]
Dialogue: 0.1:54:29.07.1:54:30.86.Default..0.0.0..- [Judy gasping for air]\N- No! Judy!
Dialogue: 0.1:54:30.95.1:54:32.58.Default..0.0.0..[sputtering]
Dialogue: 0.1:54:32.66.1:54:34.87.Default..0.0.0..Ed! The knife! Ed.
Dialogue: 0.1:54:35.74.1:54:36.79.Default..0.0.0..[Ed exclaims]
Dialogue: 0.1:54:38.21.1:54:39.46.Default..0.0.0..[wailing]
Dialogue: 0.1:54:41.88.1:54:42.67.Default..0.0.0..[straining]
Dialogue: 0.1:54:45.71.1:54:46.42.Default..0.0.0..Oh…
Dialogue: 0.1:54:47.42.1:54:48.80.Default..0.0.0..[screams] No!
Dialogue: 0.1:54:49.76.1:54:51.01.Default..0.0.0..- [rope creaking]\N- [Ed grunting]
Dialogue: 0.1:54:51.09.1:54:53.10.Default..0.0.0..[shrieks]
Dialogue: 0.1:54:54.14.1:54:55.39.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine] Ed!
Dialogue: 0.1:54:55.47.1:54:56.68.Default..0.0.0..Get her down!
Dialogue: 0.1:54:56.77.1:54:59.44.Default..0.0.0..- [Ed] Tony! Lift her up!\N- Get her down! Get her down!
Dialogue: 0.1:54:59.52.1:55:02.61.Default..0.0.0..- Oh. my God! Judy! Judy!\N- [Tony] Oh. God! [grunting]
Dialogue: 0.1:55:03.81.1:55:05.40.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine wailing]
Dialogue: 0.1:55:05.73.1:55:06.86.Default..0.0.0..[screams]
Dialogue: 0.1:55:07.82.1:55:10.78.Default..0.0.0..- Oh. my God! Judy!\N- [Tony straining]
Dialogue: 0.1:55:10.86.1:55:11.82.Default..0.0.0..[grunts]
Dialogue: 0.1:55:12.91.1:55:13.87.Default..0.0.0..Come on!
Dialogue: 0.1:55:19.79.1:55:21.08.Default..0.0.0..[straining]
Dialogue: 0.1:55:21.17.1:55:22.04.Default..0.0.0..Judy!
Dialogue: 0.1:55:25.09.1:55:25.84.Default..0.0.0..[Ed yelps]
Dialogue: 0.1:55:27.25.1:55:28.26.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine screams]
Dialogue: 0.1:55:28.34.1:55:29.42.Default..0.0.0..[screams]
Dialogue: 0.1:55:29.72.1:55:30.42.Default..0.0.0..[cries out]
Dialogue: 0.1:55:31.01.1:55:32.34.Default..0.0.0..[Tony groans]
Dialogue: 0.1:55:32.89.1:55:34.89.Default..0.0.0..[Ed wheezes. coughs]
Dialogue: 0.1:55:36.06.1:55:37.68.Default..0.0.0..- [Tony grunts]\N- [Ed wheezes]
Dialogue: 0.1:55:37.77.1:55:39.56.Default..0.0.0..- Hang on. Okay. Okay.\N- [Ed coughs]
Dialogue: 0.1:55:39.64.1:55:40.85.Default..0.0.0..[Tony murmuring]
Dialogue: 0.1:55:43.60.1:55:45.52.Default..0.0.0..- She's not got a pulse.\N- [Ed] No.
Dialogue: 0.1:55:45.61.1:55:47.48.Default..0.0.0..Get outta the way.\NJust get outta the way!
Dialogue: 0.1:55:47.57.1:55:49.49.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:55:54.20.1:55:55.74.Default..0.0.0..- Ed. I can help!\N- I got it!
Dialogue: 0.1:55:56.33.1:55:58.20.Default..0.0.0..- I've got it!\N- Judy…
Dialogue: 0.1:55:58.29.1:56:00.20.Default..0.0.0..- Oh. God! No!\N- Come on. baby. Come on. baby. please.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:00.29.1:56:01.87.Default..0.0.0..- Come on. Judy.\N- Please. please.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:01.96.1:56:04.04.Default..0.0.0..- No! Oh. my baby! My baby!\N- Come on. honey.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:04.12.1:56:05.25.Default..0.0.0..Come on. baby.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:05.33.1:56:06.63.Default..0.0.0..- You can do this.\N- Please. Lord!
Dialogue: 0.1:56:07.21.1:56:09.25.Default..0.0.0..Please. don't take her. Please. God.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:09.34.1:56:10.21.Default..0.0.0..Please.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:10.30.1:56:11.63.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine sobs]
Dialogue: 0.1:56:11.72.1:56:13.47.Default..0.0.0..[sniffling]
Dialogue: 0.1:56:19.56.1:56:20.56.Default..0.0.0..No…
Dialogue: 0.1:56:22.06.1:56:24.02.Default..0.0.0..- [heart thudding]\N- [sputtering. choking]
Dialogue: 0.1:56:24.31.1:56:26.15.Default..0.0.0..- Ed?\N- I can't-- Keep going.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:26.23.1:56:27.31.Default..0.0.0..Okay.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:27.40.1:56:28.77.Default..0.0.0..[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0.1:56:29.78.1:56:31.69.Default..0.0.0..[wails] Oh. Father!
Dialogue: 0.1:56:32.28.1:56:33.36.Default..0.0.0..One. two.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:33.74.1:56:35.16.Default..0.0.0..[Tony grunting]
Dialogue: 0.1:56:35.24.1:56:36.12.Default..0.0.0..Come on!
Dialogue: 0.1:56:36.20.1:56:37.53.Default..0.0.0..[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0.1:56:37.62.1:56:38.99.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:56:40.20.1:56:41.12.Default..0.0.0..Come on.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:41.70.1:56:42.62.Default..0.0.0..[groans]
Dialogue: 0.1:56:44.79.1:56:46.25.Default..0.0.0..[gasps. coughs]
Dialogue: 0.1:56:47.25.1:56:48.84.Default..0.0.0..- Oh. God!\N- [hacking coughs]
Dialogue: 0.1:56:48.92.1:56:51.34.Default..0.0.0..Thank you! Thank you. God. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:51.42.1:56:52.34.Default..0.0.0..Judy.
Dialogue: 0.1:56:52.67.1:56:54.68.Default..0.0.0..[sobbing]
Dialogue: 0.1:56:55.26.1:56:56.80.Default..0.0.0..[creaking]
Dialogue: 0.1:57:01.27.1:57:03.27.Default..0.0.0..- [thunder clap]\N- [panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:57:08.23.1:57:09.27.Default..0.0.0..Mom?
Dialogue: 0.1:57:10.36.1:57:11.40.Default..0.0.0..Dad?
Dialogue: 0.1:57:22.37.1:57:23.91.Default..0.0.0..[shouting]
Dialogue: 0.1:57:25.16.1:57:26.62.Default..0.0.0..[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0.1:57:27.46.1:57:28.29.Default..0.0.0..Ed.
Dialogue: 0.1:57:29.59.1:57:30.50.Default..0.0.0..Stop it!
Dialogue: 0.1:57:34.42.1:57:35.92.Default..0.0.0..In the name of the Father.\Nthe Son. and the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0.1:57:36.80.1:57:39.76.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}In nomine Patris. et Filii.{\i0}\N{\i1}et Spiritus Sancti.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:57:43.35.1:57:45.89.Default..0.0.0..We cast you out. Every unclean spirit!
Dialogue: 0.1:57:47.14.1:57:47.98.Default..0.0.0..[creature wails]
Dialogue: 0.1:57:48.06.1:57:49.73.Default..0.0.0..Every satanic power!
Dialogue: 0.1:57:49.81.1:57:50.77.Default..0.0.0..Every legion!
Dialogue: 0.1:57:51.61.1:57:54.07.Default..0.0.0..And by the power of our Lord Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0.1:57:57.24.1:58:00.66.Default..0.0.0..[Ed panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:58:04.16.1:58:05.41.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine yelps]
Dialogue: 0.1:58:05.50.1:58:06.41.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine] Ed!
Dialogue: 0.1:58:06.71.1:58:10.08.Default..0.0.0..[wind blowing]
Dialogue: 0.1:58:11.59.1:58:13.50.Default..0.0.0..- [fabric tearing]\N- [yells]
Dialogue: 0.1:58:15.05.1:58:18.05.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Omnem potentiam satanicam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:58:18.13.1:58:19.05.Default..0.0.0..[squelching]
Dialogue: 0.1:58:19.13.1:58:22.64.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Incursionem adversarii infernalis!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:58:22.93.1:58:24.39.Default..0.0.0..♪ {\i1}Lucy Locket… {\i0}♪
Dialogue: 0.1:58:24.47.1:58:28.14.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Omnem legionem et sectam diabolicam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:58:28.23.1:58:31.10.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- In nomine et virtute!{\i0}\N- [screams]
Dialogue: 0.1:58:31.86.1:58:33.07.Default..0.0.0..[demonic voice] Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0.1:58:35.15.1:58:36.07.Default..0.0.0..[gasps]
Dialogue: 0.1:58:37.90.1:58:38.90.Default..0.0.0..[cries out]
Dialogue: 0.1:58:39.49.1:58:40.95.Default..0.0.0..[snarls]
Dialogue: 0.1:58:43.03.1:58:44.83.Default..0.0.0..- [groans]\N- No!
Dialogue: 0.1:58:45.29.1:58:45.95.Default..0.0.0..[gasps]
Dialogue: 0.1:58:47.04.1:58:49.00.Default..0.0.0..- Ed!\N- You're gonna watch him die.
Dialogue: 0.1:58:49.08.1:58:50.79.Default..0.0.0..I command you with the word of God!
Dialogue: 0.1:58:51.38.1:58:54.17.Default..0.0.0..[gasping] You're not there.
Dialogue: 0.1:58:54.25.1:58:56.71.Default..0.0.0..You're not there. You're not there.
Dialogue: 0.1:58:57.84.1:58:59.68.Default..0.0.0..[sobbing] They won't go away.
Dialogue: 0.1:58:59.76.1:59:03.39.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- ♪ Lucy Locket lost her pocket ♪{\i0}\N{\i1}- ♪ Lucy Locket lost her pocket ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:59:03.47.1:59:06.39.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- ♪ Kitty Fisher found it ♪{\i0}\N{\i1}- ♪ Kitty Fisher found it ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:59:06.81.1:59:09.73.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- ♪ Not a penny was there in it ♪{\i0}\N{\i1}- ♪ Not a penny was there in it ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:59:09.81.1:59:12.60.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- ♪ Only ribbon 'round it ♪{\i0}\N{\i1}- ♪ Only ribbon 'round it ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.1:59:13.06.1:59:15.86.Default..0.0.0..You can shut it out. Just shut it out.
Dialogue: 0.1:59:17.94.1:59:18.86.Default..0.0.0..Get her outta here!
Dialogue: 0.1:59:21.11.1:59:21.91.Default..0.0.0..No.
Dialogue: 0.1:59:24.49.1:59:26.41.Default..0.0.0..[Ed straining]
Dialogue: 0.1:59:28.54.1:59:29.87.Default..0.0.0..[groans]
Dialogue: 0.1:59:30.58.1:59:32.33.Default..0.0.0..- [strains]\N- [Lorraine grunts]
Dialogue: 0.1:59:32.83.1:59:34.25.Default..0.0.0..[low snarling]
Dialogue: 0.1:59:37.05.1:59:38.51.Default..0.0.0..[Judy panting]
Dialogue: 0.1:59:38.59.1:59:40.01.Default..0.0.0..Don't look away.
Dialogue: 0.1:59:40.09.1:59:41.09.Default..0.0.0..[strains]
Dialogue: 0.1:59:42.55.1:59:44.09.Default..0.0.0..Don't shut it out.
Dialogue: 0.1:59:45.64.1:59:47.60.Default..0.0.0..Mom. [sobs]
Dialogue: 0.1:59:51.52.1:59:53.52.Default..0.0.0..Don't run!
Dialogue: 0.1:59:53.77.1:59:55.27.Default..0.0.0..[thunder rumbling]
Dialogue: 0.2:00:00.11.2:00:02.11.Default..0.0.0..[glass trembling]
Dialogue: 0.2:00:09.37.2:00:11.37.Default..0.0.0..[screams]
Dialogue: 0.2:00:15.54.2:00:16.92.Default..0.0.0..[snarling]
Dialogue: 0.2:00:17.63.2:00:19.00.Default..0.0.0..[Judy and Lorraine grunting]
Dialogue: 0.2:00:19.09.2:00:19.92.Default..0.0.0..[grunts]
Dialogue: 0.2:00:33.23.2:00:34.73.Default..0.0.0..[straining]
Dialogue: 0.2:00:34.81.2:00:36.19.Default..0.0.0..[wails]
Dialogue: 0.2:00:38.36.2:00:39.36.Default..0.0.0..You're…
Dialogue: 0.2:00:39.44.2:00:40.98.Default..0.0.0..not…
Dialogue: 0.2:00:41.07.2:00:42.32.Default..0.0.0..- …there.\N- [shrieks]
Dialogue: 0.2:00:44.66.2:00:46.28.Default..0.0.0..[Simon barking]
Dialogue: 0.2:00:46.37.2:00:47.53.Default..0.0.0..[Smurls gasping]
Dialogue: 0.2:00:47.62.2:00:49.20.Default..0.0.0..[thunder rumbling]
Dialogue: 0.2:00:51.37.2:00:53.29.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.2:00:53.37.2:00:54.96.Default..0.0.0..[gasping]
Dialogue: 0.2:01:01.84.2:01:02.80.Default..0.0.0..[Ed exhales]
Dialogue: 0.2:01:02.88.2:01:04.88.Default..0.0.0..[Judy sobbing]
Dialogue: 0.2:01:36.42.2:01:37.50.Default..0.0.0..Bye. Judy.
Dialogue: 0.2:01:54.39.2:01:56.02.Default..0.0.0..[grunting]
Dialogue: 0.2:01:56.39.2:01:57.23.Default..0.0.0..[sighs]
Dialogue: 0.2:02:00.44.2:02:02.11.Default..0.0.0..- [Tony] Good?\N- Good.
Dialogue: 0.2:02:02.98.2:02:04.11.Default..0.0.0..[exhales]
Dialogue: 0.2:02:04.74.2:02:06.45.Default..0.0.0..[panting]
Dialogue: 0.2:02:07.36.2:02:08.53.Default..0.0.0..All right.
Dialogue: 0.2:02:32.76.2:02:34.77.Default..0.0.0..[keys jingle]
Dialogue: 0.2:02:39.02.2:02:39.77.Default..0.0.0..Hey.
Dialogue: 0.2:02:50.74.2:02:52.20.Default..0.0.0..Welcome to the family.
Dialogue: 0.2:03:05.34.2:03:07.05.Default..0.0.0..[door creaks]
Dialogue: 0.2:03:08.55.2:03:09.51.Default..0.0.0..[lock turning]
Dialogue: 0.2:03:09.59.2:03:10.63.Default..0.0.0..[lock clicks]
Dialogue: 0.2:03:15.85.2:03:17.85.Default..0.0.0..[organ playing wedding procession]
Dialogue: 0.2:03:41.25.2:03:42.87.Default..0.0.0..So beautiful.
Dialogue: 0.2:03:56.30.2:03:57.14.Default..0.0.0..[soft chuckle]
Dialogue: 0.2:04:08.82.2:04:10.24.Default..0.0.0..You may kiss the bride.
Dialogue: 0.2:04:12.32.2:04:14.32.Default..0.0.0..[congregation cheers. applauds]
Dialogue: 0.2:04:17.66.2:04:19.24.Default..0.0.0..[laughs]
Dialogue: 0.2:04:19.33.2:04:22.12.Default..0.0.0..[cheers]
Dialogue: 0.2:04:27.29.2:04:28.88.Default..0.0.0..["Comfort You" by Van Morrison playing]
Dialogue: 0.2:04:29.30.2:04:30.88.Default..0.0.0..[children laughing]
Dialogue: 0.2:04:31.63.2:04:36.93.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}♪ I wanna comfort you ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.2:04:39.01.2:04:44.98.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}♪ I wanna comfort you ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.2:04:46.02.2:04:51.94.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}♪ I wanna comfort you ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.2:04:53.36.2:04:55.28.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}♪ Just let your tears… ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.2:04:55.36.2:04:57.24.Default..0.0.0..I had a vision last night.
Dialogue: 0.2:04:57.99.2:04:58.99.Default..0.0.0..Yeah?
Dialogue: 0.2:04:59.37.2:05:01.24.Default..0.0.0..- Mm.\N- What was it?
Dialogue: 0.2:05:02.04.2:05:03.33.Default..0.0.0..Our future.
Dialogue: 0.2:05:03.41.2:05:07.46.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}♪ Like when you were a child ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.2:05:07.54.2:05:08.84.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}♪ I'll do what I can do ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.2:05:08.92.2:05:12.46.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine] {\i1}I dreamed{\i0}\N{\i1}that we became grandparents.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.2:05:12.55.2:05:13.63.Default..0.0.0..- [Ed] {\i1}Oh.{\i0}\N- [Lorraine chuckles]
Dialogue: 0.2:05:13.72.2:05:16.72.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine] {\i1}And that baby's{\i0}\N{\i1}definitely gonna get spoiled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.2:05:16.80.2:05:18.01.Default..0.0.0..[Ed chuckles]
Dialogue: 0.2:05:18.09.2:05:19.47.Default..0.0.0..[laughs]
Dialogue: 0.2:05:20.68.2:05:23.18.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine] {\i1}We finally got around{\i0}\N{\i1}to writing our book…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.2:05:24.14.2:05:26.10.Default..0.0.0..- …and it was terrible.\N- [snorts. chuckles]
Dialogue: 0.2:05:27.15.2:05:28.31.Default..0.0.0..[inaudible]
Dialogue: 0.2:05:29.19.2:05:31.40.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine] {\i1}But it shared{\i0}\N{\i1}the story of our family…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.2:05:32.57.2:05:34.65.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}and all those{\i0}\N{\i1}that we met along the way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.2:05:34.74.2:05:35.78.Default..0.0.0..[inaudible]
Dialogue: 0.2:05:36.57.2:05:39.57.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine] {\i1}And we still passed on{\i0}\N{\i1}what we learned to a new generation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.2:05:46.62.2:05:49.42.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}And we never stopped having adventures.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.2:05:54.17.2:05:55.13.Default..0.0.0..[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0.2:05:57.63.2:06:00.18.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine] {\i1}And we never stopped{\i0}\N{\i1}helping people…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.2:06:01.47.2:06:04.64.Default..0.0.0..…even when the only thing we could do\Nwas talk to them on the phone.
Dialogue: 0.2:06:10.27.2:06:11.86.Default..0.0.0..[Lorraine] {\i1}And then we were old.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.2:06:13.78.2:06:17.65.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}And Judy and Tony{\i0}\N{\i1}were visiting us with their kids.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.2:06:19.28.2:06:21.03.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}And they brought their kids.{\i0}
